CLASS zcl_solution DEFINITION
  PUBLIC
  FINAL
  CREATE PUBLIC.

  PUBLIC SECTION.
    CLASS-METHODS solution
      IMPORTING
        lst TYPE STANDARD TABLE
      RETURNING
        VALUE(result) TYPE i.
ENDCLASS.

CLASS zcl_solution IMPLEMENTATION.
  METHOD solution.
    FIELD-SYMBOLS <lst> TYPE ANY TABLE.
    ASSIGN lst TO <lst>.

    result = 0.

    DATA idx TYPE i VALUE 0.
    FIELD-SYMBOLS <row> TYPE any.
    FIELD-SYMBOLS <comp> TYPE any.

    LOOP AT <lst> ASSIGNING <row>.
      idx = idx + 1.

      "Even positions in the original task are 0-based (2nd, 4th, ...)
      IF ( idx - 1 ) MOD 2 <> 0.
        CONTINUE.
      ENDIF.

      UNASSIGN <comp>.
      ASSIGN <row> TO <comp>.
      IF sy-subrc <> 0.
        CONTINUE.
      ENDIF.

      IF cl_abap_typedescr=>describe_by_data( <row> )->type_kind = cl_abap_typedescr=>typekind_struct1
         OR cl_abap_typedescr=>describe_by_data( <row> )->type_kind = cl_abap_typedescr=>typekind_struct2.
        ASSIGN COMPONENT 1 OF STRUCTURE <row> TO <comp>.
        IF sy-subrc <> 0.
          CONTINUE.
        ENDIF.
      ENDIF.

      TRY.
          DATA(lv_i) = CONV i( <comp> ).
          IF lv_i MOD 2 <> 0.
            result = result + lv_i.
          ENDIF.
        CATCH cx_sy_conversion_no_number cx_sy_move_cast_error.
      ENDTRY.
    ENDLOOP.
  ENDMETHOD.
ENDCLASS.

CLASS zcl_move_one_ball DEFINITION
  PUBLIC
  FINAL
  CREATE PUBLIC.

  PUBLIC SECTION.
    TYPES ty_int_tab TYPE STANDARD TABLE OF int8 WITH DEFAULT KEY.

    CLASS-METHODS move_one_ball
      IMPORTING
        it_arr       TYPE ty_int_tab
      RETURNING
        VALUE(rv_ok) TYPE abap_bool.
ENDCLASS.

CLASS zcl_move_one_ball IMPLEMENTATION.
  METHOD move_one_ball.
    DATA lt_arr TYPE ty_int_tab.
    lt_arr = it_arr.

    DATA(lv_n) = lines( lt_arr ).
    IF lv_n <= 1.
      rv_ok = abap_true.
      RETURN.
    ENDIF.

    DATA lv_breaks TYPE i VALUE 0.
    DATA lv_prev   TYPE int8.
    DATA lv_curr   TYPE int8.

    READ TABLE lt_arr INDEX 1 INTO lv_prev.
    DO lv_n - 1 TIMES.
      READ TABLE lt_arr INDEX sy-index + 1 INTO lv_curr.
      IF lv_prev > lv_curr.
        lv_breaks = lv_breaks + 1.
        IF lv_breaks > 1.
          rv_ok = abap_false.
          RETURN.
        ENDIF.
      ENDIF.
      lv_prev = lv_curr.
    ENDDO.

    READ TABLE lt_arr INDEX 1 INTO DATA(lv_first).
    READ TABLE lt_arr INDEX lv_n INTO DATA(lv_last).

    IF lv_breaks = 0.
      rv_ok = abap_true.
    ELSE.
      rv_ok = xsdbool( lv_last <= lv_first ).
    ENDIF.
  ENDMETHOD.
ENDCLASS.

CLASS zcl_move_one_ball DEFINITION
  PUBLIC
  FINAL
  CREATE PUBLIC.

  PUBLIC SECTION.
    CLASS-METHODS move_one_ball
      IMPORTING
        it_arr TYPE ANY TABLE
      RETURNING
        VALUE(rv_possible) TYPE abap_bool.
ENDCLASS.

CLASS zcl_move_one_ball IMPLEMENTATION.
  METHOD move_one_ball.
    rv_possible = abap_true.

    DATA(lv_n) = lines( it_arr ).
    IF lv_n <= 1.
      RETURN.
    ENDIF.

    DATA lt_arr TYPE STANDARD TABLE OF i WITH DEFAULT KEY.
    DATA lt_sorted TYPE STANDARD TABLE OF i WITH DEFAULT KEY.

    FIELD-SYMBOLS <row> TYPE any.
    FIELD-SYMBOLS <val> TYPE any.

    LOOP AT it_arr ASSIGNING <row>.
      ASSIGN <row> TO <val>.
      APPEND CONV i( <val> ) TO lt_arr.
    ENDLOOP.

    lt_sorted = lt_arr.
    SORT lt_sorted ASCENDING.

    IF lt_arr = lt_sorted.
      RETURN.
    ENDIF.

    DATA(lv_breaks) = 0.
    DATA(lv_idx) = 2.

    WHILE lv_idx <= lv_n.
      IF lt_arr[ lv_idx - 1 ] > lt_arr[ lv_idx ].
        lv_breaks = lv_breaks + 1.
        IF lv_breaks > 1.
          rv_possible = abap_false.
          RETURN.
        ENDIF.
      ENDIF.
      lv_idx = lv_idx + 1.
    ENDWHILE.

    IF lt_arr[ lv_n ] > lt_arr[ 1 ].
      lv_breaks = lv_breaks + 1.
    ENDIF.

    IF lv_breaks = 0.
      rv_possible = abap_true.
    ELSEIF lv_breaks = 1.
      IF lt_arr[ lv_n ] < lt_arr[ 1 ].
        rv_possible = abap_false.
      ENDIF.
    ELSE.
      rv_possible = abap_false.
    ENDIF.
  ENDMETHOD.
ENDCLASS.

CLASS zcl_move_one_ball DEFINITION
  PUBLIC
  FINAL
  CREATE PUBLIC.

  PUBLIC SECTION.
    CLASS-METHODS move_one_ball
      IMPORTING
        it_arr TYPE ANY TABLE
      RETURNING
        VALUE(rv_possible) TYPE abap_bool.
ENDCLASS.

CLASS zcl_move_one_ball IMPLEMENTATION.
  METHOD move_one_ball.
    DATA lv_n TYPE i.
    lv_n = lines( it_arr ).

    IF lv_n <= 1.
      rv_possible = abap_true.
      RETURN.
    ENDIF.

    FIELD-SYMBOLS <row> TYPE any.
    DATA lt_values TYPE STANDARD TABLE OF string WITH EMPTY KEY.

    LOOP AT it_arr ASSIGNING <row>.
      APPEND |{ <row> }| TO lt_values.
    ENDLOOP.

    DATA lt_sorted TYPE STANDARD TABLE OF string WITH EMPTY KEY.
    lt_sorted = lt_values.
    SORT lt_sorted BY table_line.

    DATA lv_breaks TYPE i VALUE 0.
    DATA lv_idx TYPE i.
    DATA lv_curr TYPE string.
    DATA lv_next TYPE string.

    DO lv_n TIMES.
      lv_idx = sy-index.

      READ TABLE lt_values INDEX lv_idx INTO lv_curr.
      IF lv_idx = lv_n.
        READ TABLE lt_values INDEX 1 INTO lv_next.
      ELSE.
        READ TABLE lt_values INDEX lv_idx + 1 INTO lv_next.
      ENDIF.

      IF lv_curr > lv_next.
        lv_breaks = lv_breaks + 1.
        IF lv_breaks > 1.
          rv_possible = abap_false.
          RETURN.
        ENDIF.
      ENDIF.
    ENDDO.

    IF lv_breaks = 0.
      rv_possible = xsdbool( lt_values = lt_sorted ).
      RETURN.
    ENDIF.

    DATA lv_min TYPE string.
    READ TABLE lt_sorted INDEX 1 INTO lv_min.

    DATA lv_pos_min TYPE i VALUE 0.
    DO lv_n TIMES.
      READ TABLE lt_values INDEX sy-index INTO lv_curr.
      IF lv_curr = lv_min.
        lv_pos_min = sy-index.
        EXIT.
      ENDIF.
    ENDDO.

    IF lv_pos_min = 0.
      rv_possible = abap_false.
      RETURN.
    ENDIF.

    DATA lv_shift TYPE i.
    lv_shift = lv_n - lv_pos_min + 1.

    DATA lt_rot TYPE STANDARD TABLE OF string WITH EMPTY KEY.
    DATA lv_src_idx TYPE i.

    DO lv_n TIMES.
      lv_idx = sy-index.
      lv_src_idx = lv_idx - lv_shift.
      WHILE lv_src_idx <= 0.
        lv_src_idx = lv_src_idx + lv_n.
      ENDWHILE.
      READ TABLE lt_values INDEX lv_src_idx INTO lv_curr.
      APPEND lv_curr TO lt_rot.
    ENDDO.

    rv_possible = xsdbool( lt_rot = lt_sorted ).
  ENDMETHOD.
ENDCLASS.

CLASS zcl_move_one_ball DEFINITION
  PUBLIC
  FINAL
  CREATE PUBLIC.

  PUBLIC SECTION.
    TYPES ty_int_tab TYPE STANDARD TABLE OF i WITH EMPTY KEY.

    CLASS-METHODS move_one_ball
      IMPORTING
        it_arr TYPE ty_int_tab
      RETURNING
        VALUE(rv_possible) TYPE abap_bool.
ENDCLASS.

CLASS zcl_move_one_ball IMPLEMENTATION.
  METHOD move_one_ball.
    DATA lt_sorted TYPE ty_int_tab.
    DATA lv_n      TYPE i.
    DATA lv_breaks TYPE i.
    DATA lv_i      TYPE i.

    FIELD-SYMBOLS <a> TYPE i.
    FIELD-SYMBOLS <b> TYPE i.

    lv_n = lines( it_arr ).
    IF lv_n <= 1.
      rv_possible = abap_true.
      RETURN.
    ENDIF.

    lt_sorted = it_arr.
    SORT lt_sorted ASCENDING.
    IF lt_sorted = it_arr.
      rv_possible = abap_true.
      RETURN.
    ENDIF.

    lv_breaks = 0.

    DO lv_n - 1 TIMES.
      lv_i = sy-index.
      ASSIGN it_arr[ lv_i ] TO <a>.
      ASSIGN it_arr[ lv_i + 1 ] TO <b>.
      IF <a> > <b>.
        lv_breaks = lv_breaks + 1.
        IF lv_breaks > 1.
          rv_possible = abap_false.
          RETURN.
        ENDIF.
      ENDIF.
    ENDDO.

    ASSIGN it_arr[ lv_n ] TO <a>.
    ASSIGN it_arr[ 1 ] TO <b>.
    IF <a> > <b>.
      lv_breaks = lv_breaks + 1.
    ENDIF.

    rv_possible = xsdbool( lv_breaks <= 1 ).
  ENDMETHOD.
ENDCLASS.

CLASS zcl_move_one_ball DEFINITION
  PUBLIC
  FINAL
  CREATE PUBLIC.

  PUBLIC SECTION.
    CLASS-METHODS move_one_ball
      IMPORTING
        it_arr       TYPE STANDARD TABLE
      RETURNING
        VALUE(rv_ok) TYPE abap_bool.
ENDCLASS.

CLASS zcl_move_one_ball IMPLEMENTATION.
  METHOD move_one_ball.
    rv_ok = abap_true.

    FIELD-SYMBOLS <lt_arr> TYPE ANY TABLE.
    ASSIGN it_arr TO <lt_arr>.
    IF sy-subrc <> 0 OR <lt_arr> IS INITIAL.
      RETURN.
    ENDIF.

    DATA(lv_n) = lines( <lt_arr> ).
    IF lv_n <= 1.
      RETURN.
    ENDIF.

    DATA lt_vals TYPE STANDARD TABLE OF i WITH EMPTY KEY.
    FIELD-SYMBOLS <lv_any> TYPE any.
    LOOP AT <lt_arr> ASSIGNING <lv_any>.
      APPEND CONV i( <lv_any> ) TO lt_vals.
    ENDLOOP.

    DATA(lv_breaks) = 0.

    DATA lv_prev TYPE i.
    READ TABLE lt_vals INDEX 1 INTO lv_prev.

    DATA lv_idx TYPE i VALUE 2.
    DATA lv_curr TYPE i.
    WHILE lv_idx <= lv_n.
      READ TABLE lt_vals INDEX lv_idx INTO lv_curr.
      IF lv_prev > lv_curr.
        lv_breaks = lv_breaks + 1.
        IF lv_breaks > 1.
          rv_ok = abap_false.
          RETURN.
        ENDIF.
      ENDIF.
      lv_prev = lv_curr.
      lv_idx = lv_idx + 1.
    ENDWHILE.

    IF lv_breaks = 0.
      rv_ok = abap_true.
      RETURN.
    ENDIF.

    DATA lv_first TYPE i.
    DATA lv_last  TYPE i.
    READ TABLE lt_vals INDEX 1 INTO lv_first.
    READ TABLE lt_vals INDEX lv_n INTO lv_last.

    IF lv_last <= lv_first.
      rv_ok = abap_true.
    ELSE.
      rv_ok = abap_false.
    ENDIF.
  ENDMETHOD.
ENDCLASS.

CLASS zcl_move_one_ball DEFINITION
  PUBLIC
  FINAL
  CREATE PUBLIC.

  PUBLIC SECTION.
    CLASS-METHODS move_one_ball
      IMPORTING
        it_arr TYPE ANY TABLE
      RETURNING
        VALUE(rv_possible) TYPE abap_bool.
ENDCLASS.

CLASS zcl_move_one_ball IMPLEMENTATION.
  METHOD move_one_ball.
    rv_possible = abap_true.

    FIELD-SYMBOLS <t> TYPE ANY TABLE.
    ASSIGN it_arr TO <t>.
    IF <t> IS NOT ASSIGNED.
      RETURN.
    ENDIF.

    DATA(lv_n) = lines( <t> ).
    IF lv_n <= 1.
      RETURN.
    ENDIF.

    DATA lt_vals TYPE STANDARD TABLE OF string WITH EMPTY KEY.
    FIELD-SYMBOLS <v> TYPE any.

    LOOP AT <t> ASSIGNING <v>.
      APPEND |{ <v> }| TO lt_vals.
    ENDLOOP.

    DATA lt_sorted TYPE STANDARD TABLE OF string WITH EMPTY KEY.
    lt_sorted = lt_vals.
    SORT lt_sorted BY table_line.

    DATA lv_breaks TYPE i VALUE 0.
    DATA lv_prev TYPE string.
    DATA lv_curr TYPE string.

    LOOP AT lt_vals INTO lv_curr.
      IF sy-tabix = 1.
        lv_prev = lv_curr.
        CONTINUE.
      ENDIF.

      IF lv_prev > lv_curr.
        lv_breaks = lv_breaks + 1.
        IF lv_breaks > 1.
          rv_possible = abap_false.
          RETURN.
        ENDIF.
      ENDIF.

      lv_prev = lv_curr.
    ENDLOOP.

    READ TABLE lt_vals INDEX 1 INTO DATA(lv_first).
    READ TABLE lt_vals INDEX lv_n INTO DATA(lv_last).

    IF lv_breaks = 1 AND lv_last > lv_first.
      rv_possible = abap_false.
      RETURN.
    ENDIF.

    READ TABLE lt_sorted INDEX 1 INTO DATA(lv_min).

    DATA lv_pos_min TYPE i VALUE 0.
    LOOP AT lt_vals INTO lv_curr.
      IF lv_curr = lv_min.
        lv_pos_min = sy-tabix.
        EXIT.
      ENDIF.
    ENDLOOP.

    DATA lt_rot TYPE STANDARD TABLE OF string WITH EMPTY KEY.

    IF lv_pos_min > 1.
      LOOP AT lt_vals INTO lv_curr FROM lv_pos_min TO lv_n.
        APPEND lv_curr TO lt_rot.
      ENDLOOP.
      LOOP AT lt_vals INTO lv_curr FROM 1 TO lv_pos_min - 1.
        APPEND lv_curr TO lt_rot.
      ENDLOOP.
    ELSE.
      lt_rot = lt_vals.
    ENDIF.

    IF lt_rot <> lt_sorted.
      rv_possible = abap_false.
    ENDIF.
  ENDMETHOD.
ENDCLASS.

CLASS zcl_count_nums DEFINITION
  PUBLIC
  FINAL
  CREATE PUBLIC.

  PUBLIC SECTION.
    TYPES ty_int_tab TYPE STANDARD TABLE OF int8 WITH EMPTY KEY.

    CLASS-METHODS count_nums
      IMPORTING
        it_arr TYPE ty_int_tab
      RETURNING
        VALUE(rv_count) TYPE int8.
ENDCLASS.

CLASS zcl_count_nums IMPLEMENTATION.
  METHOD count_nums.
    rv_count = 0.

    LOOP AT it_arr INTO DATA(lv_num).
      DATA(lv_work) = lv_num.
      DATA(lv_sum) TYPE int8 VALUE 0.

      IF lv_work = 0.
        CONTINUE.
      ENDIF.

      IF lv_work < 0.
        lv_sum = lv_sum - 1.
        lv_work = abs( lv_work ).
      ENDIF.

      WHILE lv_work > 0.
        lv_sum = lv_sum + ( lv_work MOD 10 ).
        lv_work = lv_work DIV 10.
      ENDWHILE.

      IF lv_sum > 0.
        rv_count = rv_count + 1.
      ENDIF.
    ENDLOOP.
  ENDMETHOD.
ENDCLASS.

CLASS zcl_count_nums DEFINITION
  PUBLIC
  FINAL
  CREATE PUBLIC.

  PUBLIC SECTION.
    CLASS-METHODS count_nums
      IMPORTING
        it_arr TYPE ANY TABLE
      RETURNING
        VALUE(rv_count) TYPE i.
ENDCLASS.

CLASS zcl_count_nums IMPLEMENTATION.
  METHOD count_nums.
    DATA: lv_num_i TYPE i,
          lv_abs   TYPE i,
          lv_sign  TYPE i,
          lv_sum   TYPE i,
          lv_digit TYPE i.

    FIELD-SYMBOLS: <lv_any> TYPE any.

    rv_count = 0.

    LOOP AT it_arr ASSIGNING <lv_any>.
      CLEAR lv_num_i.
      TRY.
          lv_num_i = CONV i( <lv_any> ).
        CATCH cx_sy_conversion_no_number cx_sy_move_cast_error cx_sy_conversion_overflow.
          CONTINUE.
      ENDTRY.

      lv_abs  = lv_num_i.
      lv_sign = 1.
      lv_sum  = 0.

      IF lv_abs < 0.
        lv_sign = -1.
        lv_abs  = lv_abs * -1.
      ENDIF.

      IF lv_abs = 0.
        lv_sum = 0.
      ELSE.
        WHILE lv_abs > 0.
          lv_digit = lv_abs MOD 10.
          lv_abs   = lv_abs DIV 10.
          lv_sum   = lv_sum + lv_digit.
        ENDWHILE.
        lv_sum = lv_sum + lv_sign.
      ENDIF.

      IF lv_sum > 0.
        rv_count = rv_count + 1.
      ENDIF.
    ENDLOOP.
  ENDMETHOD.
ENDCLASS.

CLASS zcl_count_nums DEFINITION
  PUBLIC
  FINAL
  CREATE PUBLIC.

  PUBLIC SECTION.
    CLASS-METHODS count_nums
      IMPORTING
        it_arr TYPE ANY TABLE
      RETURNING
        VALUE(rv_count) TYPE i.
ENDCLASS.

CLASS zcl_count_nums IMPLEMENTATION.
  METHOD count_nums.
    rv_count = 0.

    FIELD-SYMBOLS <lv_any> TYPE any.

    LOOP AT it_arr ASSIGNING <lv_any>.
      DATA(lv_num) = 0.

      TRY.
          lv_num = CONV i( <lv_any> ).
        CATCH cx_root.
          CONTINUE.
      ENDTRY.

      DATA(lv_work) = abs( lv_num ).
      DATA(lv_sum)  = 0.

      IF lv_work = 0.
        IF lv_num > 0.
          rv_count = rv_count + 1.
        ENDIF.
        CONTINUE.
      ENDIF.

      DATA(lv_first_abs) = lv_work.
      WHILE lv_first_abs >= 10.
        lv_first_abs = lv_first_abs DIV 10.
      ENDWHILE.

      IF lv_num < 0.
        lv_sum = lv_sum - lv_first_abs.
      ELSE.
        lv_sum = lv_sum + lv_first_abs.
      ENDIF.

      WHILE lv_work >= 10.
        lv_sum = lv_sum + ( lv_work MOD 10 ).
        lv_work = lv_work DIV 10.
      ENDWHILE.

      IF lv_sum > 0.
        rv_count = rv_count + 1.
      ENDIF.
    ENDLOOP.
  ENDMETHOD.
ENDCLASS.

CLASS zcl_count_nums DEFINITION
  PUBLIC
  FINAL
  CREATE PUBLIC.

  PUBLIC SECTION.
    TYPES ty_num_tab TYPE STANDARD TABLE OF i WITH EMPTY KEY.

    CLASS-METHODS count_nums
      IMPORTING
        it_arr TYPE ty_num_tab
      RETURNING
        VALUE(rv_count) TYPE i.
ENDCLASS.

CLASS zcl_count_nums IMPLEMENTATION.
  METHOD count_nums.
    DATA lv_num   TYPE i.
    DATA lv_abs   TYPE i.
    DATA lv_sign  TYPE i.
    DATA lv_str   TYPE string.
    DATA lv_sum   TYPE i.
    DATA lv_len   TYPE i.
    DATA lv_pos   TYPE i.
    DATA lv_char  TYPE c LENGTH 1.
    DATA lv_digit TYPE i.

    rv_count = 0.

    LOOP AT it_arr INTO lv_num.
      lv_sign = 1.
      IF lv_num < 0.
        lv_sign = -1.
        lv_abs  = lv_num * -1.
      ELSE.
        lv_abs  = lv_num.
      ENDIF.

      lv_str = lv_abs.
      lv_len = strlen( lv_str ).
      lv_sum = 0.

      lv_pos = 0.
      WHILE lv_pos < lv_len.
        lv_char = lv_str+lv_pos(1).
        lv_digit = lv_char.

        IF lv_pos = 0.
          lv_sum = lv_sum + ( lv_sign * lv_digit ).
        ELSE.
          lv_sum = lv_sum + lv_digit.
        ENDIF.

        lv_pos = lv_pos + 1.
      ENDWHILE.

      IF lv_sum > 0.
        rv_count = rv_count + 1.
      ENDIF.
    ENDLOOP.
  ENDMETHOD.
ENDCLASS.

CLASS zcl_count_nums DEFINITION
  PUBLIC
  FINAL
  CREATE PUBLIC.

  PUBLIC SECTION.
    CLASS-METHODS count_nums
      IMPORTING
        it_arr TYPE STANDARD TABLE OF syindex
      RETURNING
        VALUE(rv_count) TYPE syindex.
ENDCLASS.

CLASS zcl_count_nums IMPLEMENTATION.
  METHOD count_nums.
    DATA: lv_num   TYPE i,
          lv_sum   TYPE i,
          lv_neg   TYPE abap_bool,
          lv_s     TYPE string,
          lv_idx   TYPE i,
          lv_len   TYPE i,
          lv_char  TYPE c LENGTH 1,
          lv_digit TYPE i.

    FIELD-SYMBOLS: <n> TYPE syindex.

    rv_count = 0.

    LOOP AT it_arr ASSIGNING <n>.
      lv_num = <n>.
      lv_sum = 0.
      lv_neg = abap_false.

      IF lv_num = 0.
        CONTINUE.
      ENDIF.

      IF lv_num < 0.
        lv_neg = abap_true.
        lv_num = abs( lv_num ).
      ENDIF.

      lv_s = lv_num.
      lv_len = strlen( lv_s ).

      DO lv_len TIMES.
        lv_idx = sy-index - 1.
        lv_char = lv_s+lv_idx(1).
        lv_digit = lv_char.

        IF lv_idx = 0 AND lv_neg = abap_true.
          lv_digit = 0 - lv_digit.
        ENDIF.

        lv_sum = lv_sum + lv_digit.
      ENDDO.

      IF lv_sum > 0.
        rv_count = rv_count + 1.
      ENDIF.
    ENDLOOP.
  ENDMETHOD.
ENDCLASS.

CLASS zcl_count_nums DEFINITION
  PUBLIC
  FINAL
  CREATE PUBLIC.

  PUBLIC SECTION.
    CLASS-METHODS count_nums
      IMPORTING
        it_arr TYPE STANDARD TABLE
      RETURNING
        VALUE(rv_count) TYPE i.
ENDCLASS.

CLASS zcl_count_nums IMPLEMENTATION.
  METHOD count_nums.
    rv_count = 0.

    FIELD-SYMBOLS <n> TYPE any.

    LOOP AT it_arr ASSIGNING <n>.
      DATA lv_n TYPE i.
      DATA lv_sum TYPE i.
      DATA lv_sign TYPE i.
      DATA lv_digit TYPE i.
      DATA lv_first TYPE abap_bool.

      lv_n = <n>.
      lv_sum = 0.

      IF lv_n = 0.
        CONTINUE.
      ENDIF.

      lv_sign = 1.
      IF lv_n < 0.
        lv_sign = -1.
        lv_n = lv_n * -1.
      ENDIF.

      lv_first = abap_true.

      WHILE lv_n > 0.
        lv_digit = lv_n MOD 10.
        lv_n = lv_n DIV 10.

        IF lv_first = abap_true.
          lv_sum = lv_sum + ( lv_sign * lv_digit ).
          lv_first = abap_false.
        ELSE.
          lv_sum = lv_sum + lv_digit.
        ENDIF.
      ENDWHILE.

      IF lv_sum > 0.
        rv_count = rv_count + 1.
      ENDIF.
    ENDLOOP.
  ENDMETHOD.
ENDCLASS.

CLASS zcl_count_nums DEFINITION
  PUBLIC
  FINAL
  CREATE PUBLIC.

  PUBLIC SECTION.
    CLASS-METHODS count_nums
      IMPORTING
        it_arr TYPE ANY TABLE
      RETURNING
        VALUE(rv_count) TYPE i.
ENDCLASS.

CLASS zcl_count_nums IMPLEMENTATION.
  METHOD count_nums.
    FIELD-SYMBOLS: <lv_any> TYPE any.

    DATA: lv_num     TYPE i,
          lv_abs     TYPE i,
          lv_sum     TYPE i,
          lv_first   TYPE abap_bool,
          lv_digit   TYPE i.

    rv_count = 0.

    LOOP AT it_arr ASSIGNING <lv_any>.
      TRY.
          lv_num = CONV i( <lv_any> ).
        CATCH cx_sy_conversion_no_number cx_sy_conversion_overflow.
          CONTINUE.
      ENDTRY.

      lv_sum = 0.
      lv_abs = abs( lv_num ).
      lv_first = abap_true.

      IF lv_abs = 0.
        lv_sum = 0.
      ELSE.
        WHILE lv_abs > 0.
          lv_digit = lv_abs MOD 10.
          lv_abs = lv_abs DIV 10.

          IF lv_first = abap_true AND lv_num < 0.
            lv_sum = lv_sum - lv_digit.
            lv_first = abap_false.
          ELSE.
            lv_sum = lv_sum + lv_digit.
            lv_first = abap_false.
          ENDIF.
        ENDWHILE.
      ENDIF.

      IF lv_sum > 0.
        rv_count = rv_count + 1.
      ENDIF.
    ENDLOOP.
  ENDMETHOD.
ENDCLASS.

CLASS zcl_count_nums DEFINITION
  PUBLIC
  FINAL
  CREATE PRIVATE.

  PUBLIC SECTION.
    CLASS-METHODS count_nums
      IMPORTING
        it_arr TYPE STANDARD TABLE
      RETURNING
        VALUE(rv_count) TYPE i.
ENDCLASS.

CLASS zcl_count_nums IMPLEMENTATION.
  METHOD count_nums.
    DATA lv_num   TYPE i.
    DATA lv_work  TYPE i.
    DATA lv_sum   TYPE i.
    DATA lv_digit TYPE i.

    FIELD-SYMBOLS <lv_any> TYPE any.

    rv_count = 0.

    LOOP AT it_arr ASSIGNING <lv_any>.
      lv_num = <lv_any>.
      lv_work = lv_num.
      lv_sum  = 0.

      IF lv_work = 0.
        CONTINUE.
      ENDIF.

      WHILE lv_work <> 0.
        lv_digit = lv_work MOD 10.
        lv_sum   = lv_sum + lv_digit.
        lv_work  = lv_work DIV 10.
      ENDWHILE.

      IF lv_sum > 0.
        rv_count = rv_count + 1.
      ENDIF.
    ENDLOOP.
  ENDMETHOD.
ENDCLASS.

CLASS zcl_count_nums DEFINITION
  PUBLIC
  FINAL
  CREATE PUBLIC.

  PUBLIC SECTION.
    TYPES ty_i_tab TYPE STANDARD TABLE OF i WITH EMPTY KEY.

    CLASS-METHODS count_nums
      IMPORTING
        it_arr TYPE ty_i_tab
      RETURNING
        VALUE(rv_count) TYPE i.
ENDCLASS.

CLASS zcl_count_nums IMPLEMENTATION.
  METHOD count_nums.
    DATA lv_sum         TYPE i.
    DATA lv_num         TYPE i.
    DATA lv_abs         TYPE i.
    DATA lv_str         TYPE string.
    DATA lv_len         TYPE i.
    DATA lv_pos         TYPE i.
    DATA lv_char        TYPE c LENGTH 1.
    DATA lv_digit       TYPE i.
    DATA lv_first_char  TYPE c LENGTH 1.
    DATA lv_first_digit TYPE i.

    FIELD-SYMBOLS <n> TYPE i.

    rv_count = 0.

    LOOP AT it_arr ASSIGNING <n>.
      lv_sum = 0.
      lv_num = <n>.

      lv_abs = lv_num.
      IF lv_abs < 0.
        lv_abs = lv_abs * -1.
      ENDIF.

      lv_str = |{ lv_abs }|.
      lv_len = strlen( lv_str ).

      DO lv_len TIMES.
        lv_pos = sy-index - 1.
        lv_char = lv_str+lv_pos(1).
        lv_digit = cl_abap_conv_in_ce=>uccpi( CONV string( lv_char ) ) - cl_abap_conv_in_ce=>uccpi( `0` ).
        lv_sum = lv_sum + lv_digit.
      ENDDO.

      IF lv_num < 0 AND lv_len > 0.
        lv_first_char = lv_str(1).
        lv_first_digit = cl_abap_conv_in_ce=>uccpi( CONV string( lv_first_char ) ) - cl_abap_conv_in_ce=>uccpi( `0` ).
        lv_sum = lv_sum - ( 2 * lv_first_digit ).
      ENDIF.

      IF lv_sum > 0.
        rv_count = rv_count + 1.
      ENDIF.
    ENDLOOP.
  ENDMETHOD.
ENDCLASS.

CLASS zcl_count_nums DEFINITION
  PUBLIC
  FINAL
  CREATE PUBLIC.

  PUBLIC SECTION.
    CLASS-METHODS count_nums
      IMPORTING
        it_arr TYPE ANY TABLE
      RETURNING
        VALUE(rv_count) TYPE i.
ENDCLASS.

CLASS zcl_count_nums IMPLEMENTATION.
  METHOD count_nums.
    DATA: lv_num   TYPE i,
          lv_n     TYPE i,
          lv_sum   TYPE i,
          lv_digit TYPE i.

    FIELD-SYMBOLS <ls_row> TYPE any.
    FIELD-SYMBOLS <lv_val> TYPE any.

    rv_count = 0.

    LOOP AT it_arr ASSIGNING <ls_row>.
      CLEAR lv_num.

      ASSIGN <ls_row> TO <lv_val>.
      IF sy-subrc = 0 AND <lv_val> IS ASSIGNED.
        TRY.
            lv_num = <lv_val>.
          CATCH cx_sy_move_cast_error cx_sy_conversion_error cx_sy_conversion_no_number.
            CONTINUE.
        ENDTRY.
      ELSE.
        CONTINUE.
      ENDIF.

      lv_n = lv_num.
      lv_sum = 0.

      IF lv_n <> 0.
        WHILE lv_n <> 0.
          lv_digit = lv_n MOD 10.
          lv_sum = lv_sum + lv_digit.
          lv_n = lv_n DIV 10.
        ENDWHILE.
      ENDIF.

      IF lv_sum > 0.
        rv_count = rv_count + 1.
      ENDIF.
    ENDLOOP.
  ENDMETHOD.
ENDCLASS.

CLASS zcl_maximum_k DEFINITION
  PUBLIC
  FINAL
  CREATE PRIVATE.

  PUBLIC SECTION.
    TYPES ty_int_tab TYPE STANDARD TABLE OF i WITH NON-UNIQUE SORTED KEY k1 COMPONENTS table_line.
    TYPES ty_result  TYPE STANDARD TABLE OF i WITH EMPTY KEY.

    CLASS-METHODS maximum
      IMPORTING
        it_arr TYPE ty_int_tab
        iv_k   TYPE i
      RETURNING
        VALUE(rt_result) TYPE ty_result.
ENDCLASS.

CLASS zcl_maximum_k IMPLEMENTATION.
  METHOD maximum.
    rt_result = VALUE ty_result( ).

    IF iv_k <= 0 OR lines( it_arr ) = 0.
      RETURN.
    ENDIF.

    DATA lt_sorted TYPE ty_int_tab.
    lt_sorted = it_arr.
    SORT lt_sorted BY table_line.

    DATA(lv_len) = lines( lt_sorted ).
    DATA(lv_k) = iv_k.
    IF lv_k > lv_len.
      lv_k = lv_len.
    ENDIF.

    DATA(lv_start) = lv_len - lv_k + 1.

    LOOP AT lt_sorted INTO DATA(lv_val) FROM lv_start.
      APPEND lv_val TO rt_result.
    ENDLOOP.
  ENDMETHOD.
ENDCLASS.

CLASS zcl_maximum_k DEFINITION
  PUBLIC
  FINAL
  CREATE PUBLIC.

  PUBLIC SECTION.
    TYPES ty_int_tab TYPE STANDARD TABLE OF i WITH DEFAULT KEY.

    CLASS-METHODS maximum
      IMPORTING
        arr           TYPE ty_int_tab
        k             TYPE i
      RETURNING
        VALUE(result) TYPE ty_int_tab.
ENDCLASS.

CLASS zcl_maximum_k IMPLEMENTATION.
  METHOD maximum.
    DATA lv_k    TYPE i.
    DATA lv_len  TYPE i.
    DATA lv_from TYPE i.
    DATA lv_idx  TYPE i.

    lv_k = k.
    IF lv_k < 0.
      lv_k = 0.
    ENDIF.

    DATA lt_sorted TYPE ty_int_tab.
    lt_sorted = arr.
    SORT lt_sorted ASCENDING.

    lv_len = lines( lt_sorted ).
    IF lv_k > lv_len.
      lv_k = lv_len.
    ENDIF.

    IF lv_k = 0.
      RETURN.
    ENDIF.

    lv_from = lv_len - lv_k + 1.

    lv_idx = 0.
    LOOP AT lt_sorted ASSIGNING FIELD-SYMBOL(<v>).
      lv_idx = lv_idx + 1.
      IF lv_idx >= lv_from.
        APPEND <v> TO result.
      ENDIF.
    ENDLOOP.
  ENDMETHOD.
ENDCLASS.

CLASS zcl_maximum_k DEFINITION
  PUBLIC
  FINAL
  CREATE PUBLIC.

  PUBLIC SECTION.
    TYPES ty_result TYPE STANDARD TABLE OF i WITH EMPTY KEY.

    CLASS-METHODS maximum
      IMPORTING
        arr TYPE ANY TABLE
        k   TYPE i
      RETURNING
        VALUE(rt_result) TYPE ty_result.
ENDCLASS.

CLASS zcl_maximum_k IMPLEMENTATION.
  METHOD maximum.
    DATA: lv_k   TYPE i,
          lv_len TYPE i,
          lt_all TYPE ty_result,
          lv_val TYPE i.

    FIELD-SYMBOLS <row> TYPE any.

    rt_result = VALUE ty_result( ).

    lv_k = k.
    IF lv_k <= 0.
      RETURN.
    ENDIF.

    LOOP AT arr ASSIGNING <row>.
      APPEND CONV i( <row> ) TO lt_all.
    ENDLOOP.

    lv_len = lines( lt_all ).
    IF lv_k > lv_len.
      lv_k = lv_len.
    ENDIF.

    SORT lt_all BY table_line DESCENDING.

    LOOP AT lt_all INTO lv_val FROM 1 TO lv_k.
      APPEND lv_val TO rt_result.
    ENDLOOP.

    SORT rt_result BY table_line ASCENDING.
  ENDMETHOD.
ENDCLASS.

CLASS zcl_maximum_k DEFINITION
  PUBLIC
  FINAL
  CREATE PUBLIC.

  PUBLIC SECTION.
    TYPES ty_int_tab TYPE STANDARD TABLE OF i WITH NON-UNIQUE SORTED KEY sk COMPONENTS table_line.

    CLASS-METHODS maximum
      IMPORTING
        it_arr TYPE ty_int_tab
        iv_k   TYPE i
      RETURNING
        VALUE(rt_result) TYPE zcl_maximum_k=>ty_int_tab.
ENDCLASS.

CLASS zcl_maximum_k IMPLEMENTATION.
  METHOD maximum.
    rt_result = VALUE zcl_maximum_k=>ty_int_tab( ).

    IF iv_k <= 0 OR lines( it_arr ) = 0.
      RETURN.
    ENDIF.

    DATA lt_sorted TYPE zcl_maximum_k=>ty_int_tab.
    lt_sorted = it_arr.
    SORT lt_sorted ASCENDING.

    DATA lv_lines TYPE i.
    DATA lv_start TYPE i.

    lv_lines = lines( lt_sorted ).
    lv_start = lv_lines - iv_k + 1.
    IF lv_start < 1.
      lv_start = 1.
    ENDIF.

    rt_result = VALUE zcl_maximum_k=>ty_int_tab(
      FOR idx = lv_start UNTIL idx > lv_lines
      ( lt_sorted[ idx ] ) ).
  ENDMETHOD.
ENDCLASS.

CLASS zcl_maximum_k DEFINITION
  PUBLIC
  FINAL
  CREATE PUBLIC.

  PUBLIC SECTION.
    TYPES ty_result TYPE STANDARD TABLE OF i WITH EMPTY KEY.

    CLASS-METHODS maximum
      IMPORTING
        arr TYPE ANY TABLE
        k   TYPE i
      RETURNING
        VALUE(rt_max) TYPE ty_result.
ENDCLASS.

CLASS zcl_maximum_k IMPLEMENTATION.
  METHOD maximum.
    rt_max = VALUE #( ).

    IF k <= 0 OR arr IS INITIAL.
      RETURN.
    ENDIF.

    FIELD-SYMBOLS <arr> TYPE ANY TABLE.
    ASSIGN arr TO <arr>.

    DATA lt_int TYPE ty_result.

    FIELD-SYMBOLS <row> TYPE any.
    LOOP AT <arr> ASSIGNING <row>.
      APPEND CONV i( <row> ) TO lt_int.
    ENDLOOP.

    IF lt_int IS INITIAL.
      RETURN.
    ENDIF.

    DATA(lv_k) = k.
    IF lv_k > lines( lt_int ).
      lv_k = lines( lt_int ).
    ENDIF.

    SORT lt_int BY table_line DESCENDING.

    LOOP AT lt_int ASSIGNING FIELD-SYMBOL(<v>).
      IF lines( rt_max ) >= lv_k.
        EXIT.
      ENDIF.
      APPEND <v> TO rt_max.
    ENDLOOP.

    SORT rt_max BY table_line ASCENDING.
  ENDMETHOD.
ENDCLASS.

CLASS zcl_check_last_char_letter DEFINITION
  PUBLIC
  FINAL
  CREATE PUBLIC.

  PUBLIC SECTION.
    CLASS-METHODS check_if_last_char_is_a_letter
      IMPORTING
        txt TYPE string
      RETURNING
        VALUE(rv_result) TYPE abap_bool.
ENDCLASS.

CLASS zcl_check_last_char_letter IMPLEMENTATION.
  METHOD check_if_last_char_is_a_letter.
    DATA: lv_len          TYPE i,
          lv_last_idx     TYPE i,
          lv_prev_idx     TYPE i,
          lv_last         TYPE c LENGTH 1,
          lv_prev         TYPE c LENGTH 1,
          lv_has_space    TYPE abap_bool,
          lv_letters      TYPE string VALUE 'ABCDEFGHIJKLMNOPQRSTUVWXYZabcdefghijklmnopqrstuvwxyz'.

    rv_result = abap_false.

    IF txt IS INITIAL.
      RETURN.
    ENDIF.

    lv_len = strlen( txt ).
    IF lv_len <= 0.
      RETURN.
    ENDIF.

    lv_last_idx = lv_len - 1.
    lv_last = txt+lv_last_idx(1).

    IF lv_last = ` `.
      RETURN.
    ENDIF.

    IF lv_last NA lv_letters.
      RETURN.
    ENDIF.

    lv_has_space = abap_false.
    IF txt CA ` `.
      lv_has_space = abap_true.
    ENDIF.

    IF lv_len = 1.
      rv_result = abap_true.
      RETURN.
    ENDIF.

    lv_prev_idx = lv_len - 2.
    lv_prev = txt+lv_prev_idx(1).

    IF lv_prev = ` `
       OR lv_has_space = abap_false.
      rv_result = abap_true.
    ENDIF.
  ENDMETHOD.
ENDCLASS.

CLASS zcl_check_last_char_letter DEFINITION
  PUBLIC
  FINAL
  CREATE PUBLIC.

  PUBLIC SECTION.
    CLASS-METHODS check_if_last_char_is_a_letter
      IMPORTING
        iv_txt TYPE string
      RETURNING
        VALUE(rv_result) TYPE abap_bool.
ENDCLASS.

CLASS zcl_check_last_char_letter IMPLEMENTATION.
  METHOD check_if_last_char_is_a_letter.
    DATA lv_len TYPE i.
    DATA lv_off TYPE i.
    DATA lv_last TYPE c LENGTH 1.
    DATA lv_before_last TYPE c LENGTH 1.

    rv_result = abap_false.

    IF iv_txt IS INITIAL.
      RETURN.
    ENDIF.

    lv_len = strlen( iv_txt ).
    IF lv_len <= 0.
      RETURN.
    ENDIF.

    lv_off = lv_len - 1.
    lv_last = iv_txt+lv_off(1).
    IF lv_last = space.
      RETURN.
    ENDIF.

    IF lv_last CA 'ABCDEFGHIJKLMNOPQRSTUVWXYZabcdefghijklmnopqrstuvwxyz'.
      " ok
    ELSE.
      RETURN.
    ENDIF.

    IF lv_len < 2.
      RETURN.
    ENDIF.

    lv_off = lv_len - 2.
    lv_before_last = iv_txt+lv_off(1).

    IF lv_before_last = space.
      rv_result = abap_true.
    ENDIF.
  ENDMETHOD.
ENDCLASS.

CLASS zcl_rescale_to_unit DEFINITION
  PUBLIC
  FINAL
  CREATE PUBLIC.

  PUBLIC SECTION.
    CLASS-METHODS rescale_to_unit
      IMPORTING
        numbers TYPE STANDARD TABLE OF f
      RETURNING
        VALUE(rt_numbers) TYPE STANDARD TABLE OF f.
ENDCLASS.

CLASS zcl_rescale_to_unit IMPLEMENTATION.
  METHOD rescale_to_unit.
    rt_numbers = VALUE #( ).

    DATA(lv_lines) = lines( numbers ).
    IF lv_lines = 0.
      RETURN.
    ENDIF.

    DATA lv_min TYPE f.
    DATA lv_max TYPE f.

    READ TABLE numbers INDEX 1 INTO lv_min.
    lv_max = lv_min.

    LOOP AT numbers ASSIGNING FIELD-SYMBOL(<n>) FROM 2.
      IF <n> < lv_min.
        lv_min = <n>.
      ENDIF.
      IF <n> > lv_max.
        lv_max = <n>.
      ENDIF.
    ENDLOOP.

    DATA lv_den TYPE f.
    lv_den = lv_max - lv_min.

    LOOP AT numbers ASSIGNING <n>.
      DATA lv_out TYPE f.
      IF lv_den = 0.
        lv_out = 0.
      ELSE.
        lv_out = ( <n> - lv_min ) / lv_den.
      ENDIF.
      APPEND lv_out TO rt_numbers.
    ENDLOOP.
  ENDMETHOD.
ENDCLASS.

CLASS zcl_rescale_to_unit DEFINITION
  PUBLIC
  FINAL
  CREATE PUBLIC.

  PUBLIC SECTION.
    CLASS-METHODS rescale_to_unit
      IMPORTING
        numbers        TYPE STANDARD TABLE OF fltp WITH DEFAULT KEY
      RETURNING
        VALUE(result)  TYPE STANDARD TABLE OF fltp WITH DEFAULT KEY.
ENDCLASS.

CLASS zcl_rescale_to_unit IMPLEMENTATION.
  METHOD rescale_to_unit.
    DATA min_val TYPE fltp.
    DATA max_val TYPE fltp.

    READ TABLE numbers INDEX 1 INTO min_val.
    max_val = min_val.

    LOOP AT numbers ASSIGNING FIELD-SYMBOL(<n>).
      IF <n> < min_val.
        min_val = <n>.
      ENDIF.
      IF <n> > max_val.
        max_val = <n>.
      ENDIF.
    ENDLOOP.

    DATA range TYPE fltp.
    range = max_val - min_val.

    CLEAR result.

    IF range = 0.
      LOOP AT numbers ASSIGNING <n>.
        APPEND 0 TO result.
      ENDLOOP.
      RETURN.
    ENDIF.

    LOOP AT numbers ASSIGNING <n>.
      APPEND ( <n> - min_val ) / range TO result.
    ENDLOOP.
  ENDMETHOD.
ENDCLASS.

CLASS zcl_rescale_to_unit DEFINITION
  PUBLIC
  FINAL
  CREATE PUBLIC.

  PUBLIC SECTION.
    TYPES ty_num     TYPE p LENGTH 16 DECIMALS 10.
    TYPES ty_num_tab TYPE STANDARD TABLE OF ty_num WITH EMPTY KEY.

    CLASS-METHODS rescale_to_unit
      IMPORTING
        numbers TYPE ty_num_tab
      RETURNING
        VALUE(result) TYPE ty_num_tab.
ENDCLASS.

CLASS zcl_rescale_to_unit IMPLEMENTATION.
  METHOD rescale_to_unit.
    result = VALUE #( ).

    DATA lv_min   TYPE ty_num.
    DATA lv_max   TYPE ty_num.
    DATA lv_range TYPE ty_num.

    IF lines( numbers ) = 0.
      RETURN.
    ENDIF.

    READ TABLE numbers INDEX 1 INTO lv_min.
    lv_max = lv_min.

    LOOP AT numbers INTO DATA(lv_num).
      IF lv_num < lv_min.
        lv_min = lv_num.
      ENDIF.
      IF lv_num > lv_max.
        lv_max = lv_num.
      ENDIF.
    ENDLOOP.

    lv_range = lv_max - lv_min.

    IF lv_range = 0.
      LOOP AT numbers INTO DATA(lv_num2).
        APPEND CONV ty_num( 0 ) TO result.
      ENDLOOP.
      RETURN.
    ENDIF.

    LOOP AT numbers INTO DATA(lv_num3).
      APPEND ( ( lv_num3 - lv_min ) / lv_range ) TO result.
    ENDLOOP.
  ENDMETHOD.
ENDCLASS.

CLASS zcl_rescale_to_unit DEFINITION
  PUBLIC
  FINAL
  CREATE PUBLIC.

  PUBLIC SECTION.
    TYPES ty_float TYPE p LENGTH 16 DECIMALS 14.
    TYPES ty_numbers TYPE STANDARD TABLE OF ty_float WITH EMPTY KEY.

    CLASS-METHODS rescale_to_unit
      IMPORTING
        numbers        TYPE ty_numbers
      RETURNING
        VALUE(result)  TYPE ty_numbers.
ENDCLASS.

CLASS zcl_rescale_to_unit IMPLEMENTATION.
  METHOD rescale_to_unit.
    DATA: lv_min   TYPE ty_float,
          lv_max   TYPE ty_float,
          lv_range TYPE ty_float,
          lv_value TYPE ty_float.

    result = VALUE #( ).

    IF lines( numbers ) < 2.
      RETURN.
    ENDIF.

    READ TABLE numbers INDEX 1 INTO lv_min.
    lv_max = lv_min.

    LOOP AT numbers INTO lv_value.
      IF lv_value < lv_min.
        lv_min = lv_value.
      ENDIF.
      IF lv_value > lv_max.
        lv_max = lv_value.
      ENDIF.
    ENDLOOP.

    lv_range = lv_max - lv_min.

    IF lv_range = CONV ty_float( '0' ).
      result = VALUE #( FOR i = 1 THEN i + 1 UNTIL i > lines( numbers ) ( CONV ty_float( '0' ) ) ).
      RETURN.
    ENDIF.

    LOOP AT numbers INTO lv_value.
      APPEND ( lv_value - lv_min ) / lv_range TO result.
    ENDLOOP.
  ENDMETHOD.
ENDCLASS.

CLASS zcl_rescale_to_unit DEFINITION
  PUBLIC
  FINAL
  CREATE PUBLIC.

  PUBLIC SECTION.
    CLASS-METHODS rescale_to_unit
      IMPORTING
        numbers TYPE STANDARD TABLE OF f
      RETURNING
        VALUE(rt_numbers) TYPE STANDARD TABLE OF f.
ENDCLASS.

CLASS zcl_rescale_to_unit IMPLEMENTATION.
  METHOD rescale_to_unit.
    DATA: lv_min TYPE f,
          lv_max TYPE f,
          lv_num TYPE f,
          lv_den TYPE f.

    CLEAR rt_numbers.

    IF lines( numbers ) < 2.
      RETURN.
    ENDIF.

    READ TABLE numbers INDEX 1 INTO lv_num.
    IF sy-subrc <> 0.
      RETURN.
    ENDIF.

    lv_min = lv_num.
    lv_max = lv_num.

    LOOP AT numbers INTO lv_num.
      IF lv_num < lv_min.
        lv_min = lv_num.
      ENDIF.
      IF lv_num > lv_max.
        lv_max = lv_num.
      ENDIF.
    ENDLOOP.

    lv_den = lv_max - lv_min.

    IF lv_den = 0.
      LOOP AT numbers INTO lv_num.
        APPEND 0 TO rt_numbers.
      ENDLOOP.
      RETURN.
    ENDIF.

    LOOP AT numbers INTO lv_num.
      APPEND ( lv_num - lv_min ) / lv_den TO rt_numbers.
    ENDLOOP.
  ENDMETHOD.
ENDCLASS.

CLASS zcl_rescale_to_unit DEFINITION
  PUBLIC
  FINAL
  CREATE PUBLIC.

  PUBLIC SECTION.
    TYPES ty_numbers TYPE STANDARD TABLE OF p LENGTH 16 DECIMALS 7 WITH EMPTY KEY.

    CLASS-METHODS rescale
      IMPORTING
        numbers       TYPE ty_numbers
      RETURNING
        VALUE(result) TYPE ty_numbers.
ENDCLASS.

CLASS zcl_rescale_to_unit IMPLEMENTATION.
  METHOD rescale.
    DATA lv_min TYPE p LENGTH 16 DECIMALS 7.
    DATA lv_max TYPE p LENGTH 16 DECIMALS 7.
    DATA lv_rng TYPE p LENGTH 16 DECIMALS 7.

    result = VALUE #( ).

    IF lines( numbers ) = 0.
      RETURN.
    ENDIF.

    READ TABLE numbers INDEX 1 INTO lv_min.
    lv_max = lv_min.

    LOOP AT numbers ASSIGNING FIELD-SYMBOL(<n>).
      IF <n> < lv_min.
        lv_min = <n>.
      ENDIF.
      IF <n> > lv_max.
        lv_max = <n>.
      ENDIF.
    ENDLOOP.

    lv_rng = lv_max - lv_min.

    IF lv_rng = 0.
      LOOP AT numbers ASSIGNING <n>.
        APPEND CONV #( 0 ) TO result.
      ENDLOOP.
      RETURN.
    ENDIF.

    LOOP AT numbers ASSIGNING <n>.
      APPEND ( ( <n> - lv_min ) / lv_rng ) TO result.
    ENDLOOP.
  ENDMETHOD.

CLASS zcl_rescale_to_unit DEFINITION
  PUBLIC
  FINAL
  CREATE PUBLIC.

  PUBLIC SECTION.
    CLASS-METHODS rescale_to_unit
      IMPORTING
        numbers TYPE STANDARD TABLE OF f
      RETURNING
        VALUE(rt_numbers) TYPE STANDARD TABLE OF f.
ENDCLASS.

CLASS zcl_rescale_to_unit IMPLEMENTATION.
  METHOD rescale_to_unit.
    DATA: lv_min   TYPE f,
          lv_max   TYPE f,
          lv_range TYPE f.

    FIELD-SYMBOLS: <n> TYPE f.

    IF lines( numbers ) = 0.
      RETURN.
    ENDIF.

    READ TABLE numbers INDEX 1 INTO lv_min.
    lv_max = lv_min.

    LOOP AT numbers ASSIGNING <n>.
      IF <n> < lv_min.
        lv_min = <n>.
      ENDIF.
      IF <n> > lv_max.
        lv_max = <n>.
      ENDIF.
    ENDLOOP.

    lv_range = lv_max - lv_min.

    LOOP AT numbers ASSIGNING <n>.
      IF lv_range = 0.
        APPEND 0 TO rt_numbers.
      ELSE.
        APPEND ( ( <n> - lv_min ) / lv_range ) TO rt_numbers.
      ENDIF.
    ENDLOOP.
  ENDMETHOD.
ENDCLASS.

CLASS zcl_rescale_to_unit IMPLEMENTATION.

      RETURN.

CLASS zcl_rescale_to_unit DEFINITION
  PUBLIC
  FINAL
  CREATE PUBLIC.

  PUBLIC SECTION.
    CLASS-METHODS rescale_to_unit
      IMPORTING
        numbers        TYPE STANDARD TABLE OF f
      RETURNING
        VALUE(result)  TYPE STANDARD TABLE OF f.
ENDCLASS.

CLASS zcl_rescale_to_unit IMPLEMENTATION.
  METHOD rescale_to_unit.
    FIELD-SYMBOLS <num> TYPE f.

    DATA(min_val) = numbers[ 1 ].
    DATA(max_val) = numbers[ 1 ].

    LOOP AT numbers ASSIGNING <num>.
      IF <num> < min_val.
        min_val = <num>.
      ENDIF.
      IF <num> > max_val.
        max_val = <num>.
      ENDIF.
    ENDLOOP.

    DATA(range) = max_val - min_val.

    CLEAR result.

    IF range = 0.
      LOOP AT numbers ASSIGNING <num>.
        APPEND 0 TO result.
      ENDLOOP.
      RETURN.
    ENDIF.

    LOOP AT numbers ASSIGNING <num>.
      APPEND ( ( <num> - min_val ) / range ) TO result.
    ENDLOOP.
  ENDMETHOD.
ENDCLASS.

CLASS zcl_rescale_to_unit DEFINITION
  PUBLIC
  FINAL
  CREATE PUBLIC.

  PUBLIC SECTION.
    CLASS-METHODS rescale_to_unit
      IMPORTING
        numbers TYPE ANY TABLE
      RETURNING
        VALUE(result) TYPE STANDARD TABLE OF decfloat34 WITH EMPTY KEY.
ENDCLASS.

CLASS zcl_rescale_to_unit IMPLEMENTATION.
  METHOD rescale_to_unit.
    FIELD-SYMBOLS: <num> TYPE any.

    DATA: lv_min     TYPE decfloat34,
          lv_max     TYPE decfloat34,
          lv_val     TYPE decfloat34,
          lv_range   TYPE decfloat34,
          lv_has_val TYPE abap_bool VALUE abap_false.

    result = VALUE #( ).

    IF lines( numbers ) < 2.
      RETURN.
    ENDIF.

    LOOP AT numbers ASSIGNING <num>.
      TRY.
          lv_val = CONV decfloat34( <num> ).
        CATCH cx_sy_conversion_no_number cx_sy_conversion_overflow cx_sy_conversion_error.
          CONTINUE.
      ENDTRY.

      IF lv_has_val = abap_false.
        lv_min = lv_val.
        lv_max = lv_val.
        lv_has_val = abap_true.
      ELSE.
        IF lv_val < lv_min.
          lv_min = lv_val.
        ENDIF.
        IF lv_val > lv_max.
          lv_max = lv_val.
        ENDIF.
      ENDIF.
    ENDLOOP.

    IF lv_has_val = abap_false.
      RETURN.
    ENDIF.

    lv_range = lv_max - lv_min.

    IF lv_range = 0.
      DO lines( numbers ) TIMES.
        APPEND CONV decfloat34( 0 ) TO result.
      ENDDO.
      RETURN.
    ENDIF.

    LOOP AT numbers ASSIGNING <num>.
      lv_val = CONV decfloat34( <num> ).
      APPEND ( lv_val - lv_min ) / lv_range TO result.
    ENDLOOP.
  ENDMETHOD.
ENDCLASS.

CLASS zcl_customer_id_generator DEFINITION
  PUBLIC
  FINAL
  CREATE PUBLIC.

  PUBLIC SECTION.
    TYPES ty_country TYPE c LENGTH 50.
    TYPES ty_region  TYPE c LENGTH 100.
    TYPES ty_ctype   TYPE c LENGTH 30.

    CLASS-METHODS generate_customer_id
      IMPORTING
        country       TYPE ty_country
        region        TYPE ty_region
        customer_type TYPE ty_ctype
        digit_id      TYPE i
      RETURNING
        VALUE(customer_id) TYPE string.

ENDCLASS.

CLASS zcl_customer_id_generator IMPLEMENTATION.

  METHOD generate_customer_id.
    DATA: lv_country_in    TYPE string,
          lv_region_in     TYPE string,
          lv_type_in       TYPE string,
          lv_country_code  TYPE c LENGTH 4,
          lv_region_code   TYPE c LENGTH 2,
          lv_type_code     TYPE c LENGTH 1,
          lv_id5           TYPE c LENGTH 5,
          lv_region_tmp    TYPE string,
          lv_word          TYPE string,
          lv_char          TYPE c LENGTH 1,
          lv_len           TYPE i,
          lv_off           TYPE i.

    lv_country_in = country.
    lv_region_in  = region.
    lv_type_in    = customer_type.

    SHIFT lv_country_in LEFT DELETING LEADING space.
    SHIFT lv_country_in RIGHT DELETING TRAILING space.
    SHIFT lv_region_in LEFT DELETING LEADING space.
    SHIFT lv_region_in RIGHT DELETING TRAILING space.
    SHIFT lv_type_in LEFT DELETING LEADING space.
    SHIFT lv_type_in RIGHT DELETING TRAILING space.

    lv_country_code = 'XXXX'.
    IF lv_country_in = 'Germany'.
      lv_country_code = '0049'.
    ELSEIF lv_country_in = 'Austria'.
      lv_country_code = '0043'.
    ELSEIF lv_country_in = 'Switzerland'.
      lv_country_code = '0041'.
    ENDIF.

    lv_region_code = 'XX'.
    lv_region_tmp = lv_region_in.
    TRANSLATE lv_region_tmp USING '- '.
    TRANSLATE lv_region_tmp USING '_ '.
    CONDENSE lv_region_tmp.
    SHIFT lv_region_tmp LEFT DELETING LEADING space.
    SHIFT lv_region_tmp RIGHT DELETING TRAILING space.

    IF lv_region_tmp IS NOT INITIAL.
      lv_region_code = ''.

      WHILE lv_region_tmp IS NOT INITIAL AND strlen( lv_region_code ) < 2.
        SPLIT lv_region_tmp AT space INTO lv_word lv_region_tmp.
        SHIFT lv_word LEFT DELETING LEADING space.
        SHIFT lv_word RIGHT DELETING TRAILING space.

        IF lv_word IS NOT INITIAL.
          lv_char = lv_word+0(1).
          TRANSLATE lv_char TO UPPER CASE.
          CONCATENATE lv_region_code lv_char INTO lv_region_code IN CHARACTER MODE.
        ENDIF.

        SHIFT lv_region_tmp LEFT DELETING LEADING space.
        SHIFT lv_region_tmp RIGHT DELETING TRAILING space.
      ENDWHILE.

      IF strlen( lv_region_code ) <> 2.
        lv_region_code = 'XX'.
      ENDIF.
    ENDIF.

    lv_type_code = 'X'.
    IF lv_type_in = 'Business_ Customer'.
      lv_type_code = 'B'.
    ELSEIF lv_type_in = 'Private_Customer'.
      lv_type_code = 'P'.
    ENDIF.

    lv_id5 = '00000'.
    IF digit_id >= 0.
      WRITE digit_id TO lv_id5 LEFT-JUSTIFIED.
      CONDENSE lv_id5 NO-GAPS.
      lv_len = strlen( lv_id5 ).
      IF lv_len > 5.
        lv_off = lv_len - 5.
        lv_id5 = lv_id5+lv_off(5).
      ELSEIF lv_len < 5.
        lv_id5 = |{ lv_id5 WIDTH = 5 PAD = '0' ALIGN = RIGHT }|.
      ENDIF.
    ENDIF.

    CONCATENATE lv_country_code lv_region_code lv_type_code lv_id5 INTO customer_id IN CHARACTER MODE.
    REPLACE ALL OCCURRENCES OF space IN customer_id WITH ''.
    customer_id = customer_id+0(12).
  ENDMETHOD.

ENDCLASS.

CLASS zcl_customer_id_generator DEFINITION
  PUBLIC
  FINAL
  CREATE PUBLIC.

  PUBLIC SECTION.
    TYPES: ty_country       TYPE c LENGTH 50,
           ty_region        TYPE c LENGTH 100,
           ty_customer_type TYPE c LENGTH 30.

    CLASS-METHODS generate_customer_id
      IMPORTING
        country       TYPE ty_country
        region        TYPE ty_region
        customer_type TYPE ty_customer_type
        digit_id      TYPE i
      RETURNING
        VALUE(customer_id) TYPE string.
ENDCLASS.

CLASS zcl_customer_id_generator IMPLEMENTATION.
  METHOD generate_customer_id.
    DATA: lv_country        TYPE string,
          lv_region         TYPE string,
          lv_cust_type      TYPE string,
          lv_country_code   TYPE c LENGTH 4,
          lv_region_code    TYPE c LENGTH 2,
          lv_type_code      TYPE c LENGTH 1,
          lv_id5            TYPE c LENGTH 5,
          lv_abbr           TYPE string,
          lt_words          TYPE STANDARD TABLE OF string WITH EMPTY KEY,
          lv_word           TYPE string,
          lv_len            TYPE i,
          lv_off            TYPE i.

    lv_country_code = 'XXXX'.
    lv_region_code  = 'XX'.
    lv_type_code    = 'X'.

    lv_country   = country.
    lv_region    = region.
    lv_cust_type = customer_type.

    SHIFT lv_country LEFT DELETING LEADING space.
    SHIFT lv_country RIGHT DELETING TRAILING space.
    SHIFT lv_region LEFT DELETING LEADING space.
    SHIFT lv_region RIGHT DELETING TRAILING space.
    SHIFT lv_cust_type LEFT DELETING LEADING space.
    SHIFT lv_cust_type RIGHT DELETING TRAILING space.

    IF lv_country = 'Germany'.
      lv_country_code = '0049'.
    ELSEIF lv_country = 'Austria'.
      lv_country_code = '0043'.
    ELSEIF lv_country = 'Switzerland'.
      lv_country_code = '0041'.
    ELSE.
      lv_country_code = 'XXXX'.
    ENDIF.

    IF lv_region IS NOT INITIAL.
      SPLIT lv_region AT space INTO TABLE lt_words.
      CLEAR lv_abbr.
      LOOP AT lt_words INTO lv_word.
        IF lv_word IS INITIAL.
          CONTINUE.
        ENDIF.
        lv_abbr = lv_abbr && lv_word+0(1).
        lv_len = strlen( lv_abbr ).
        IF lv_len >= 2.
          EXIT.
        ENDIF.
      ENDLOOP.

      TRANSLATE lv_abbr TO UPPER CASE.

      lv_len = strlen( lv_abbr ).
      IF lv_len = 2.
        lv_region_code = lv_abbr(2).
      ELSE.
        lv_region_code = 'XX'.
      ENDIF.
    ELSE.
      lv_region_code = 'XX'.
    ENDIF.

    IF lv_cust_type = 'Business_ Customer'.
      lv_type_code = 'B'.
    ELSEIF lv_cust_type = 'Private_Customer'.
      lv_type_code = 'P'.
    ELSE.
      lv_type_code = 'X'.
    ENDIF.

    lv_id5 = digit_id.
    CALL FUNCTION 'CONVERSION_EXIT_ALPHA_INPUT'
      EXPORTING
        input  = lv_id5
      IMPORTING
        output = lv_id5.

    lv_len = strlen( lv_id5 ).
    IF lv_len > 5.
      lv_off = lv_len - 5.
      lv_id5 = lv_id5+lv_off(5).
    ENDIF.

    customer_id = lv_country_code && lv_region_code && lv_type_code && lv_id5.
  ENDMETHOD.
ENDCLASS.

CLASS zcl_customer_id_generator DEFINITION
  PUBLIC
  FINAL
  CREATE PUBLIC.

  PUBLIC SECTION.
    TYPES ty_country       TYPE c LENGTH 50.
    TYPES ty_region        TYPE c LENGTH 100.
    TYPES ty_customer_type TYPE c LENGTH 30.

    CLASS-METHODS generate_customer_id
      IMPORTING
        country       TYPE ty_country
        region        TYPE ty_region
        customer_type TYPE ty_customer_type
        digit_id      TYPE i
      RETURNING
        VALUE(customer_id) TYPE string.
ENDCLASS.

CLASS zcl_customer_id_generator IMPLEMENTATION.
  METHOD generate_customer_id.
    DATA: lv_country      TYPE string,
          lv_region       TYPE string,
          lv_type         TYPE string,
          lv_country_code TYPE c LENGTH 4,
          lv_region_code  TYPE c LENGTH 2,
          lv_type_code    TYPE c LENGTH 1,
          lv_id5          TYPE c LENGTH 5,
          lv_work         TYPE string,
          lv_pos          TYPE i,
          lv_found        TYPE abap_bool,
          lv_ch           TYPE c LENGTH 1.

    lv_country = country.
    lv_region  = region.
    lv_type    = customer_type.

    SHIFT lv_country LEFT DELETING LEADING space.
    SHIFT lv_country RIGHT DELETING TRAILING space.
    SHIFT lv_region LEFT DELETING LEADING space.
    SHIFT lv_region RIGHT DELETING TRAILING space.
    SHIFT lv_type LEFT DELETING LEADING space.
    SHIFT lv_type RIGHT DELETING TRAILING space.

    CASE lv_country.
      WHEN 'Germany'.
        lv_country_code = '0049'.
      WHEN 'Austria'.
        lv_country_code = '0043'.
      WHEN 'Switzerland'.
        lv_country_code = '0041'.
      WHEN OTHERS.
        lv_country_code = 'XXXX'.
    ENDCASE.

    CLEAR lv_region_code.
    lv_work = lv_region.

    SHIFT lv_work LEFT DELETING LEADING space.
    SHIFT lv_work RIGHT DELETING TRAILING space.

    lv_pos = 0.
    WHILE lv_work IS NOT INITIAL AND lv_pos < strlen( lv_work ) AND lv_region_code CP '__' = abap_false.
      IF lv_pos = 0 OR lv_work+lv_pos(1) CA ' -_/'.
        lv_found = abap_false.
        WHILE lv_pos < strlen( lv_work ) AND lv_found = abap_false.
          lv_ch = lv_work+lv_pos(1).
          IF ( lv_ch >= 'A' AND lv_ch <= 'Z' ) OR ( lv_ch >= 'a' AND lv_ch <= 'z' ).
            TRANSLATE lv_ch TO UPPER CASE.
            IF lv_region_code IS INITIAL.
              lv_region_code+0(1) = lv_ch.
            ELSEIF lv_region_code+1(1) = space.
              lv_region_code+1(1) = lv_ch.
            ENDIF.
            lv_found = abap_true.
          ENDIF.
          lv_pos = lv_pos + 1.
        ENDWHILE.
      ELSE.
        lv_pos = lv_pos + 1.
      ENDIF.
      IF lv_region_code+0(1) <> space AND lv_region_code+1(1) <> space.
        EXIT.
      ENDIF.
    ENDWHILE.

    IF lv_region_code+0(1) = space OR lv_region_code+1(1) = space.
      lv_region_code = 'XX'.
    ENDIF.

    CASE lv_type.
      WHEN 'Business_ Customer'.
        lv_type_code = 'B'.
      WHEN 'Private_Customer'.
        lv_type_code = 'P'.
      WHEN OTHERS.
        lv_type_code = 'X'.
    ENDCASE.

    lv_id5 = digit_id.
    lv_id5 = |{ digit_id WIDTH = 5 PAD = '0' }|.
    REPLACE ALL OCCURRENCES OF space IN lv_id5 WITH '0'.
    IF strlen( lv_id5 ) > 5.
      lv_id5 = lv_id5+strlen( lv_id5 )-5(5).
    ENDIF.

    customer_id = |{ lv_country_code }{ lv_region_code }{ lv_type_code }{ lv_id5 }|.
    REPLACE ALL OCCURRENCES OF space IN customer_id WITH ''.
  ENDMETHOD.
ENDCLASS.

CLASS zcl_customer_id_generator DEFINITION
  PUBLIC
  FINAL
  CREATE PUBLIC.

  PUBLIC SECTION.
    TYPES: BEGIN OF ty_country_codes,
             country_name TYPE c LENGTH 50,
             country_code TYPE c LENGTH 4,
             iso_code     TYPE c LENGTH 2,

           END OF ty_country_codes,

    TYPES: BEGIN OF ty_region_codes,
             country_code TYPE c LENGTH 4,

             region_type  TYPE c LENGTH 20,

    TYPES: BEGIN OF ty_customer_types,
             customer_type TYPE c LENGTH 30,
             type_code     TYPE c LENGTH 1,
             description   TYPE c LENGTH 100,
           END OF ty_customer_types,
           ty_t_customer_types TYPE STANDARD TABLE OF ty_customer_types WITH EMPTY KEY.

    CLASS-METHODS generate_customer_id
      IMPORTING
        country        TYPE c
        region         TYPE c
        customer_type  TYPE c
        digit_id       TYPE i

CLASS zcl_customer_id_generator IMPLEMENTATION.

  METHOD generate_customer_id.
    DATA: lv_country        TYPE string,
          lv_region         TYPE string,
          lv_customer_type  TYPE string,
          lv_country_code   TYPE string,
          lv_region_code    TYPE string,
          lv_type_code      TYPE string,
          lv_id5            TYPE string,
          lv_work           TYPE string,
          lv_abbr           TYPE string,
          lv_word           TYPE string,
          lv_c              TYPE c LENGTH 1,
          lt_words          TYPE STANDARD TABLE OF string WITH EMPTY KEY.

    lv_country = country.
    lv_region  = region.
    lv_customer_type = customer_type.

    SHIFT lv_country LEFT DELETING LEADING space.
    SHIFT lv_country RIGHT DELETING TRAILING space.
    SHIFT lv_region LEFT DELETING LEADING space.
    SHIFT lv_region RIGHT DELETING TRAILING space.
    SHIFT lv_customer_type LEFT DELETING LEADING space.
    SHIFT lv_customer_type RIGHT DELETING TRAILING space.

    lv_country_code = 'XXXX'.
    IF lv_country = 'Germany'.
      lv_country_code = '0049'.
    ELSEIF lv_country = 'Austria'.
      lv_country_code = '0043'.
    ELSEIF lv_country = 'Switzerland'.
      lv_country_code = '0041'.
    ENDIF.

    lv_region_code = 'XX'.
    IF lv_region IS NOT INITIAL.
      lv_work = lv_region.
      TRANSLATE lv_work USING '- _  '.
      DO 5 TIMES.
        REPLACE ALL OCCURRENCES OF '  ' IN lv_work WITH ' '.
      ENDDO.
      SHIFT lv_work LEFT DELETING LEADING space.
      SHIFT lv_work RIGHT DELETING TRAILING space.

      CLEAR lt_words.
      SPLIT lv_work AT space INTO TABLE lt_words.

      CLEAR lv_abbr.
      LOOP AT lt_words INTO lv_word.
        IF lv_word IS INITIAL.
          CONTINUE.
        ENDIF.
        lv_c = lv_word+0(1).
        TRANSLATE lv_c TO UPPER CASE.
        lv_abbr = lv_abbr && lv_c.
        IF strlen( lv_abbr ) >= 2.
          EXIT.
        ENDIF.
      ENDLOOP.

      IF strlen( lv_abbr ) = 2.
        lv_region_code = lv_abbr.
      ENDIF.
    ENDIF.

    lv_type_code = 'X'.
    IF lv_customer_type = 'Business_ Customer'.
      lv_type_code = 'B'.
    ELSEIF lv_customer_type = 'Private_Customer'.
      lv_type_code = 'P'.
    ENDIF.

    lv_id5 = digit_id.
    SHIFT lv_id5 LEFT DELETING LEADING space.
    WHILE strlen( lv_id5 ) < 5.
      lv_id5 = '0' && lv_id5.
    ENDWHILE.
    IF strlen( lv_id5 ) > 5.
      lv_id5 = lv_id5+0(5).
    ENDIF.

    customer_id = lv_country_code && lv_region_code && lv_type_code && lv_id5.
    REPLACE ALL OCCURRENCES OF space IN customer_id WITH ''.
    IF strlen( customer_id ) > 12.
      customer_id = customer_id+0(12).
    ENDIF.
  ENDMETHOD.

ENDCLASS.

  PUBLIC

  PUBLIC SECTION.
    CLASS-METHODS generate_customer_id

CLASS zcl_customer_id_generator IMPLEMENTATION.
  METHOD generate_customer_id.
    DATA: lv_country      TYPE string,
          lv_region       TYPE string,
          lv_type         TYPE string,
          lv_country_code TYPE c LENGTH 4,
          lv_region_code  TYPE c LENGTH 2,
          lv_type_code    TYPE c LENGTH 1,
          lv_id5          TYPE c LENGTH 5,
          lv_len          TYPE i,
          lv_char         TYPE c LENGTH 1,
          lv_prev_sep     TYPE abap_bool,
          lv_collected    TYPE string,
          lv_idx          TYPE i,
          lv_missing      TYPE i.

    lv_country = country.
    lv_region  = region.
    lv_type    = customer_type.

    SHIFT lv_country LEFT DELETING LEADING space.
    SHIFT lv_country RIGHT DELETING TRAILING space.
    SHIFT lv_region LEFT DELETING LEADING space.
    SHIFT lv_region RIGHT DELETING TRAILING space.
    SHIFT lv_type LEFT DELETING LEADING space.
    SHIFT lv_type RIGHT DELETING TRAILING space.

    CASE lv_country.
      WHEN 'Germany'.
        lv_country_code = '0049'.
      WHEN 'Austria'.
        lv_country_code = '0043'.
      WHEN 'Switzerland'.
        lv_country_code = '0041'.
      WHEN OTHERS.
        lv_country_code = 'XXXX'.
    ENDCASE.

    lv_type_code = 'X'.
    IF lv_type = 'Business_ Customer'.
      lv_type_code = 'B'.
    ELSEIF lv_type = 'Private_Customer'.
      lv_type_code = 'P'.
    ENDIF.

    lv_region_code = 'XX'.
    lv_collected = ``.
    lv_prev_sep = abap_true.

    lv_len = strlen( lv_region ).
    DO lv_len TIMES.
      lv_idx = sy-index - 1.
      lv_char = lv_region+lv_idx(1).

      IF lv_char = space OR lv_char = '-' OR lv_char = '_' OR lv_char = '.' OR lv_char = ',' OR lv_char = '/'.
        lv_prev_sep = abap_true.
        CONTINUE.
      ENDIF.

      IF lv_prev_sep = abap_true.
        TRANSLATE lv_char TO UPPER CASE.
        lv_collected = lv_collected && lv_char.
        lv_prev_sep = abap_false.
        IF strlen( lv_collected ) >= 2.
          EXIT.
        ENDIF.
      ENDIF.
    ENDDO.

    IF strlen( lv_collected ) = 2.
      lv_region_code = lv_collected(2).
    ELSE.
      lv_region_code = 'XX'.
    ENDIF.

    lv_id5 = digit_id.
    lv_len = strlen( lv_id5 ).
    IF lv_len < 5.
      lv_missing = 5 - lv_len.
      DO lv_missing TIMES.
        lv_id5 = '0' && lv_id5.
      ENDDO.
    ELSEIF lv_len > 5.
      lv_id5 = lv_id5+lv_len-5(5).
    ENDIF.

    customer_id = lv_country_code && lv_region_code && lv_type_code && lv_id5.
  ENDMETHOD.
ENDCLASS.

CLASS zcl_customer_id_generator IMPLEMENTATION.
  METHOD generate_customer_id.
    DATA: lv_country      TYPE string,
          lv_region       TYPE string,
          lv_type         TYPE string,
          lv_country_code TYPE c LENGTH 4,
          lv_region_code  TYPE c LENGTH 2,
          lv_type_code    TYPE c LENGTH 1,
          lv_id_code      TYPE c LENGTH 5,
          lv_tmp          TYPE string,
          lv_word         TYPE string,
          lt_words        TYPE STANDARD TABLE OF string WITH EMPTY KEY.

    lv_country = country.
    lv_region  = region.
    lv_type    = customer_type.

    SHIFT lv_country LEFT DELETING LEADING space.
    SHIFT lv_country RIGHT DELETING TRAILING space.
    SHIFT lv_region LEFT DELETING LEADING space.
    SHIFT lv_region RIGHT DELETING TRAILING space.
    SHIFT lv_type LEFT DELETING LEADING space.
    SHIFT lv_type RIGHT DELETING TRAILING space.

    CASE lv_country.
      WHEN 'Germany'.
        lv_country_code = '0049'.
      WHEN 'Austria'.
        lv_country_code = '0043'.
      WHEN 'Switzerland'.
        lv_country_code = '0041'.
      WHEN OTHERS.
        lv_country_code = 'XXXX'.
    ENDCASE.

    CLEAR lv_region_code.
    lv_tmp = lv_region.
    REPLACE ALL OCCURRENCES OF '-' IN lv_tmp WITH ' '.
    REPLACE ALL OCCURRENCES OF '_' IN lv_tmp WITH ' '.
    CONDENSE lv_tmp.
    SPLIT lv_tmp AT space INTO TABLE lt_words.

    LOOP AT lt_words INTO lv_word.
      SHIFT lv_word LEFT DELETING LEADING space.
      SHIFT lv_word RIGHT DELETING TRAILING space.
      IF lv_word IS INITIAL.
        CONTINUE.
      ENDIF.

      IF lv_region_code IS INITIAL.
        lv_region_code = lv_word+0(1).
      ELSEIF lv_region_code+1(1) IS INITIAL.
        lv_region_code = lv_region_code+0(1) && lv_word+0(1).
        EXIT.
      ENDIF.
    ENDLOOP.

    TRANSLATE lv_region_code TO UPPER CASE.

    IF lv_region_code IS INITIAL.
      lv_region_code = 'XX'.
    ELSEIF lv_region_code+1(1) IS INITIAL.
      lv_region_code = lv_region_code+0(1) && 'X'.
    ENDIF.

    CASE lv_type.
      WHEN 'Business_ Customer ' OR 'Business_Customer'.
        lv_type_code = 'B'.
      WHEN 'Private_Customer'.
        lv_type_code = 'P'.
      WHEN OTHERS.
        lv_type_code = 'X'.
    ENDCASE.

    lv_id_code = |{ digit_id WIDTH = 5 ALIGN = RIGHT PAD = '0' }|.

    customer_id = |{ lv_country_code }{ lv_region_code }{ lv_type_code }{ lv_id_code }|.
  ENDMETHOD.
ENDCLASS.

CLASS zcl_customer_id_generator IMPLEMENTATION.
  METHOD generate_customer_id.
    DATA: lv_country       TYPE string,
          lv_region        TYPE string,
          lv_customer_type TYPE string,
          lv_country_code  TYPE string,
          lv_region_code   TYPE string,
          lv_type_code     TYPE string,
          lv_id_5          TYPE string,
          lv_len           TYPE i,
          lv_off           TYPE i.

    lv_country       = condense( val = |{ country }| ).
    lv_region        = condense( val = |{ region }| ).
    lv_customer_type = condense( val = |{ customer_type }| ).

    CASE lv_country.
      WHEN 'Germany'.
        lv_country_code = '0049'.
      WHEN 'Austria'.
        lv_country_code = '0043'.
      WHEN 'Switzerland'.
        lv_country_code = '0041'.
      WHEN OTHERS.
        lv_country_code = 'XXXX'.
    ENDCASE.

    lv_region_code = ''.
    IF lv_region IS NOT INITIAL.
      DATA(lv_work) = lv_region.
      REPLACE ALL OCCURRENCES OF '-' IN lv_work WITH space.
      REPLACE ALL OCCURRENCES OF '_' IN lv_work WITH space.
      lv_work = condense( val = lv_work ).

      DATA lt_words TYPE STANDARD TABLE OF string WITH EMPTY KEY.
      SPLIT lv_work AT space INTO TABLE lt_words.

      LOOP AT lt_words INTO DATA(lv_word).
        IF lv_word IS INITIAL.
          CONTINUE.
        ENDIF.
        lv_region_code = lv_region_code && to_upper( lv_word(1) ).
        IF strlen( lv_region_code ) >= 2.
          EXIT.
        ENDIF.
      ENDLOOP.

      IF strlen( lv_region_code ) = 1.
        lv_region_code = lv_region_code && 'X'.
      ENDIF.
    ENDIF.

    IF lv_region_code IS INITIAL OR strlen( lv_region_code ) <> 2.
      lv_region_code = 'XX'.
    ENDIF.

    CASE lv_customer_type.
      WHEN 'Business_ Customer'.
        lv_type_code = 'B'.
      WHEN 'Private_Customer'.
        lv_type_code = 'P'.
      WHEN OTHERS.
        lv_type_code = 'X'.
    ENDCASE.

    lv_id_5 = |{ digit_id WIDTH = 5 PAD = '0' ALIGN = RIGHT }|.
    lv_len = strlen( lv_id_5 ).
    IF lv_len > 5.
      lv_off = lv_len - 5.
      lv_id_5 = lv_id_5+lv_off(5).
    ENDIF.

    customer_id = lv_country_code && lv_region_code && lv_type_code && lv_id_5.
    REPLACE ALL OCCURRENCES OF space IN customer_id WITH ''.

    lv_len = strlen( customer_id ).
    IF lv_len < 12.
      customer_id = customer_id && repeat( val = 'X' occ = 12 - lv_len ).
    ELSEIF lv_len > 12.
      customer_id = customer_id(12).
    ENDIF.
  ENDMETHOD.
ENDCLASS.

CLASS zcl_customer_id_generator IMPLEMENTATION.
  METHOD generate_customer_id.
    DATA: lv_country       TYPE string,
          lv_region        TYPE string,
          lv_customer_type TYPE string,
          lv_country_code  TYPE string,
          lv_region_code   TYPE string,
          lv_type_code     TYPE string,
          lv_id5           TYPE string,
          lv_work          TYPE string,
          lv_abbr          TYPE string,
          lv_word          TYPE string,
          lt_words         TYPE STANDARD TABLE OF string WITH DEFAULT KEY.

    lv_country       = country.
    lv_region        = region.
    lv_customer_type = customer_type.

    SHIFT lv_country LEFT DELETING LEADING space.
    SHIFT lv_country RIGHT DELETING TRAILING space.
    SHIFT lv_region LEFT DELETING LEADING space.
    SHIFT lv_region RIGHT DELETING TRAILING space.
    SHIFT lv_customer_type LEFT DELETING LEADING space.
    SHIFT lv_customer_type RIGHT DELETING TRAILING space.

    lv_country_code = 'XXXX'.
    IF lv_country = 'Germany'.
      lv_country_code = '0049'.
    ELSEIF lv_country = 'Austria'.
      lv_country_code = '0043'.
    ELSEIF lv_country = 'Switzerland'.
      lv_country_code = '0041'.
    ENDIF.

    lv_region_code = 'XX'.
    lv_work = lv_region.

    REPLACE ALL OCCURRENCES OF '-' IN lv_work WITH space.
    REPLACE ALL OCCURRENCES OF '_' IN lv_work WITH space.
    REPLACE ALL OCCURRENCES OF '/' IN lv_work WITH space.
    REPLACE ALL OCCURRENCES OF '.' IN lv_work WITH space.
    REPLACE ALL OCCURRENCES OF ',' IN lv_work WITH space.
    REPLACE ALL OCCURRENCES OF ';' IN lv_work WITH space.
    REPLACE ALL OCCURRENCES OF ':' IN lv_work WITH space.
    REPLACE ALL OCCURRENCES OF '(' IN lv_work WITH space.
    REPLACE ALL OCCURRENCES OF ')' IN lv_work WITH space.
    REPLACE ALL OCCURRENCES OF '[' IN lv_work WITH space.
    REPLACE ALL OCCURRENCES OF ']' IN lv_work WITH space.
    REPLACE ALL OCCURRENCES OF '{' IN lv_work WITH space.
    REPLACE ALL OCCURRENCES OF '}' IN lv_work WITH space.
    REPLACE ALL OCCURRENCES OF '&' IN lv_work WITH space.

    CONDENSE lv_work.

    CLEAR lt_words.
    SPLIT lv_work AT space INTO TABLE lt_words.
    DELETE lt_words WHERE table_line IS INITIAL.

    CLEAR lv_abbr.
    LOOP AT lt_words INTO lv_word.
      IF lv_word IS INITIAL.
        CONTINUE.
      ENDIF.
      lv_abbr = lv_abbr && lv_word+0(1).
      IF strlen( lv_abbr ) >= 2.
        EXIT.
      ENDIF.
    ENDLOOP.

    TRANSLATE lv_abbr TO UPPER CASE.
    IF strlen( lv_abbr ) = 2.
      lv_region_code = lv_abbr.
    ELSE.
      lv_region_code = 'XX'.
    ENDIF.

    lv_type_code = 'X'.
    IF lv_customer_type = 'Business_ Customer'.
      lv_type_code = 'B'.
    ELSEIF lv_customer_type = 'Private_Customer'.
      lv_type_code = 'P'.
    ENDIF.

    lv_id5 = digit_id.
    SHIFT lv_id5 LEFT DELETING LEADING space.
    CONDENSE lv_id5 NO-GAPS.

    IF strlen( lv_id5 ) > 5.
      lv_id5 = lv_id5+0(5).
    ELSE.
      WHILE strlen( lv_id5 ) < 5.
        lv_id5 = '0' && lv_id5.
      ENDWHILE.
    ENDIF.

    customer_id = lv_country_code && lv_region_code && lv_type_code && lv_id5.
    CONDENSE customer_id NO-GAPS.

    IF strlen( customer_id ) <> 12.
      IF strlen( customer_id ) > 12.
        customer_id = customer_id+0(12).
      ELSE.
        WHILE strlen( customer_id ) < 12.
          customer_id = customer_id && '0'.
        ENDWHILE.
      ENDIF.
    ENDIF.
  ENDMETHOD.
ENDCLASS.

    lv_country = country.
    lv_region  = region.

    TRANSLATE lv_tmp USING ': '.
    TRANSLATE lv_tmp USING '; '.

    CONDENSE lv_tmp.

    SPLIT lv_tmp AT space INTO TABLE lt_words.

    CLEAR lv_out.
    LOOP AT lt_words INTO lv_word.
      SHIFT lv_word LEFT DELETING LEADING space.
      SHIFT lv_word RIGHT DELETING TRAILING space.
      IF lv_word IS INITIAL.
        CONTINUE.
      ENDIF.
      lv_out = lv_out && lv_word+0(1).
      lv_len = strlen( lv_out ).
      IF lv_len >= 2.
        EXIT.
      ENDIF.
    ENDLOOP.

    lv_len = strlen( lv_out ).
    IF lv_len >= 2.
      lv_region_code = lv_out+0(2).
    ELSE.
      lv_region_code = 'XX'.
    ENDIF.
    TRANSLATE lv_region_code TO UPPER CASE.

    CASE lv_type.
      WHEN 'Business_ Customer'.
        lv_type_code = 'B'.
      WHEN 'Private_Customer'.
        lv_type_code = 'P'.
      WHEN OTHERS.
        lv_type_code = 'X'.
    ENDCASE.

    lv_id5 = digit_id.
    CALL FUNCTION 'CONVERSION_EXIT_ALPHA_INPUT'
      EXPORTING
        input  = lv_id5

    customer_id = lv_country_code && lv_region_code && lv_type_code && lv_id5.

    DATA lv_id5           TYPE string.

    DATA lv_region_work   TYPE string.
    DATA lv_abbr          TYPE string.
    DATA lv_word          TYPE string.
    DATA lt_words         TYPE STANDARD TABLE OF string WITH EMPTY KEY.

    lv_country       = condense( CONV string( country ) ).
    lv_region        = condense( CONV string( region ) ).
    lv_customer_type = condense( CONV string( customer_type ) ).

    IF lv_country = `Germany`.
      lv_country_code = `0049`.
    ELSEIF lv_country = `Austria`.
      lv_country_code = `0043`.
    ELSEIF lv_country = `Switzerland`.
      lv_country_code = `0041`.
    ENDIF.

    IF lv_customer_type = `Business_ Customer`.
      lv_type_code = `B`.
    ELSEIF lv_customer_type = `Private_Customer`.
      lv_type_code = `P`.
    ENDIF.

    lv_region_work = lv_region.
    REPLACE ALL OCCURRENCES OF `-` IN lv_region_work WITH ` `.
    CONDENSE lv_region_work.

    SPLIT lv_region_work AT ` ` INTO TABLE lt_words.

    CLEAR lv_abbr.
    LOOP AT lt_words INTO lv_word.
      IF lv_word IS INITIAL.
        CONTINUE.
      ENDIF.
      lv_abbr = lv_abbr && lv_word+0(1).
      IF strlen( lv_abbr ) >= 2.
        EXIT.
      ENDIF.
    ENDLOOP.

    IF strlen( lv_abbr ) = 2.
      lv_region_code = lv_abbr.
    ELSE.
      lv_region_code = `XX`.
    ENDIF.

    lv_id5 = |{ digit_id WIDTH = 5 PAD = '0' ALIGN = RIGHT }|.

    customer_id = lv_country_code && lv_region_code && lv_type_code && lv_id5.
    REPLACE ALL OCCURRENCES OF ` ` IN customer_id WITH ``.
    customer_id = customer_id+0(12).
  ENDMETHOD.
ENDCLASS.

CLASS zcl_sort_even IMPLEMENTATION.

  METHOD sort_even.
    rt_list = it_list.

    DATA lt_oddpos_values TYPE ty_i_tab.
    DATA lt_oddpos_idx    TYPE STANDARD TABLE OF sy-tabix WITH DEFAULT KEY.

    FIELD-SYMBOLS <v> TYPE i.

    LOOP AT rt_list ASSIGNING <v>.
      IF sy-tabix MOD 2 = 1.
        APPEND <v> TO lt_oddpos_values.
        APPEND sy-tabix TO lt_oddpos_idx.
      ENDIF.
    ENDLOOP.

    SORT lt_oddpos_values ASCENDING.

    DATA lv_pos TYPE i VALUE 0.
    DATA lv_val TYPE i.
    FIELD-SYMBOLS <idx> TYPE sy-tabix.

    LOOP AT lt_oddpos_idx ASSIGNING <idx>.
      lv_pos = lv_pos + 1.
      READ TABLE lt_oddpos_values INTO lv_val INDEX lv_pos.

        rt_list[ <idx> ] = lv_val.
      ENDIF.
    ENDLOOP.
  ENDMETHOD.

CLASS zcl_sort_even DEFINITION
  PUBLIC
  FINAL
  CREATE PUBLIC.

  PUBLIC SECTION.
    CLASS-METHODS sort_even
      IMPORTING
        it_list TYPE ANY TABLE
      RETURNING
        VALUE(rt_list) TYPE REF TO data.
ENDCLASS.

CLASS zcl_sort_even IMPLEMENTATION.
  METHOD sort_even.
    FIELD-SYMBOLS <lt_in>  TYPE ANY TABLE.
    FIELD-SYMBOLS <lt_out> TYPE ANY TABLE.
    FIELD-SYMBOLS <ls_in>  TYPE any.
    FIELD-SYMBOLS <ls_out> TYPE any.
    FIELD-SYMBOLS <lr_any> TYPE REF TO data.
    FIELD-SYMBOLS <lv_any> TYPE any.

    ASSIGN it_list TO <lt_in>.

    DATA(lo_tabdescr) = CAST cl_abap_tabledescr( cl_abap_typedescr=>describe_by_data( it_list ) ).
    DATA(lo_linedescr) = lo_tabdescr->get_table_line_type( ).

    CREATE DATA rt_list TYPE HANDLE lo_tabdescr.
    ASSIGN rt_list->* TO <lt_out>.
    <lt_out> = <lt_in>.

    DATA lt_even_vals TYPE STANDARD TABLE OF REF TO data WITH EMPTY KEY.
    DATA lt_even_idx  TYPE STANDARD TABLE OF i WITH EMPTY KEY.

    DATA lv_idx TYPE i VALUE 0.
    LOOP AT <lt_in> ASSIGNING <ls_in>.
      IF ( lv_idx MOD 2 ) = 0.
        APPEND ( lv_idx + 1 ) TO lt_even_idx.

        CREATE DATA DATA(lr_line) TYPE HANDLE lo_linedescr.
        ASSIGN lr_line->* TO <lv_any>.
        <lv_any> = <ls_in>.
        APPEND lr_line TO lt_even_vals.
      ENDIF.
      lv_idx = lv_idx + 1.
    ENDLOOP.

    IF lt_even_vals IS INITIAL.
      RETURN.
    ENDIF.

    DATA lt_sort_keys TYPE STANDARD TABLE OF string WITH EMPTY KEY.
    LOOP AT lt_even_vals ASSIGNING <lr_any>.
      ASSIGN <lr_any>->* TO <lv_any>.
      APPEND |{ <lv_any> }| TO lt_sort_keys.
    ENDLOOP.

    DATA lt_pos TYPE STANDARD TABLE OF i WITH EMPTY KEY.
    lt_pos = VALUE #( FOR irow = 1 THEN irow + 1 UNTIL irow > lines( lt_sort_keys ) ( irow ) ).

    SORT lt_pos STABLE BY table_line.
    SORT lt_pos STABLE BY (lt_sort_keys[ table_line ]) ASCENDING.

    DATA lt_sorted_refs TYPE STANDARD TABLE OF REF TO data WITH EMPTY KEY.
    LOOP AT lt_pos INTO DATA(lv_pos).
      APPEND lt_even_vals[ lv_pos ] TO lt_sorted_refs.
    ENDLOOP.

    DATA lv_even_pos TYPE i VALUE 0.

    lv_idx = 0.
    LOOP AT <lt_out> ASSIGNING <ls_out>.
      IF ( lv_idx MOD 2 ) = 0.
        lv_even_pos = lv_even_pos + 1.
        READ TABLE lt_sorted_refs INDEX lv_even_pos ASSIGNING <lr_any>.
        IF sy-subrc = 0.
          ASSIGN <lr_any>->* TO <lv_any>.
          <ls_out> = <lv_any>.
        ENDIF.
      ENDIF.
      lv_idx = lv_idx + 1.
    ENDLOOP.
  ENDMETHOD.
ENDCLASS.

CLASS zcl_sort_even DEFINITION
  PUBLIC
  FINAL
  CREATE PUBLIC.

  PUBLIC SECTION.
    TYPES ty_int_tab TYPE STANDARD TABLE OF i WITH NON-UNIQUE DEFAULT KEY.

CLASS zcl_sort_even IMPLEMENTATION.
  METHOD sort_even.
    DATA lv_idx      TYPE i.
    DATA lv_even_idx TYPE i.
    DATA lv_val      TYPE i.

    DATA lt_even TYPE ty_int_tab.
    DATA lv_out  TYPE i.

    rt_list = it_list.

    lv_idx = 0.
    LOOP AT it_list INTO lv_val.
      lv_idx = lv_idx + 1.
      IF ( lv_idx MOD 2 ) = 0.
        APPEND lv_val TO lt_even.
      ENDIF.
    ENDLOOP.

    SORT lt_even ASCENDING.

    lv_idx = 0.
    lv_even_idx = 0.
    LOOP AT rt_list INTO lv_out.
      lv_idx = lv_idx + 1.
      IF ( lv_idx MOD 2 ) = 0.
        lv_even_idx = lv_even_idx + 1.
        READ TABLE lt_even INTO lv_val INDEX lv_even_idx.
        IF sy-subrc = 0.
          MODIFY rt_list FROM lv_val INDEX lv_idx.
        ENDIF.
      ENDIF.
    ENDLOOP.
  ENDMETHOD.
ENDCLASS.

  PUBLIC

      IF lv_idx MOD 2 = 0.
        APPEND <v> TO lt_even.
      ENDIF.
    ENDLOOP.

    SORT lt_even ASCENDING.

    DATA lv_eidx TYPE i VALUE 0.

CLASS zcl_sort_even DEFINITION
  PUBLIC
  FINAL
  CREATE PUBLIC.

    TYPES ty_int_tab TYPE STANDARD TABLE OF ty_int WITH NON-UNIQUE DEFAULT KEY.

    CLASS-METHODS sort_even
      IMPORTING
        it_list        TYPE ty_int_tab
      RETURNING
        VALUE(rt_list) TYPE ty_int_tab.
ENDCLASS.

CLASS zcl_sort_even IMPLEMENTATION.
  METHOD sort_even.
    rt_list = it_list.

    DATA lt_even_vals TYPE ty_int_tab.
    DATA lv_idx       TYPE sy-tabix.
    DATA lv_val       TYPE ty_int.

    lv_idx = 0.
    LOOP AT it_list INTO lv_val.
      IF lv_idx MOD 2 = 0.
        APPEND lv_val TO lt_even_vals.
      ENDIF.
      lv_idx = lv_idx + 1.
    ENDLOOP.

    SORT lt_even_vals ASCENDING.

    DATA lv_even_pos TYPE sy-tabix VALUE 1.

    lv_idx = 0.
    LOOP AT rt_list ASSIGNING FIELD-SYMBOL(<lv_out>).
      IF lv_idx MOD 2 = 0.
        READ TABLE lt_even_vals INDEX lv_even_pos INTO lv_val.
        IF sy-subrc = 0.
          <lv_out> = lv_val.
          lv_even_pos = lv_even_pos + 1.

      ENDIF.

CLASS zcl_sort_even DEFINITION
  PUBLIC
  FINAL
  CREATE PUBLIC.

  PUBLIC SECTION.
    TYPES tt_int TYPE STANDARD TABLE OF i WITH DEFAULT KEY.

    CLASS-METHODS sort_even
      IMPORTING
        it_list TYPE tt_int
      RETURNING
        VALUE(rt_list) TYPE tt_int.
ENDCLASS.

CLASS zcl_sort_even IMPLEMENTATION.
  METHOD sort_even.
    DATA lt_odd  TYPE tt_int.
    DATA lt_even TYPE tt_int.
    DATA lv_val  TYPE i.

    LOOP AT it_list INTO lv_val.
      IF sy-tabix MOD 2 = 0.
        APPEND lv_val TO lt_odd.
      ELSE.
        APPEND lv_val TO lt_even.
      ENDIF.
    ENDLOOP.

    SORT lt_even ASCENDING.

    rt_list = VALUE tt_int( ).

    DATA lv_even_pos TYPE i VALUE 1.
    DATA lv_odd_pos  TYPE i VALUE 1.

    DO lines( it_list ) TIMES.
      IF sy-index MOD 2 = 0.
        READ TABLE lt_odd INTO lv_val INDEX lv_odd_pos.
        IF sy-subrc = 0.
          APPEND lv_val TO rt_list.
        ENDIF.
        lv_odd_pos = lv_odd_pos + 1.
      ELSE.
        READ TABLE lt_even INTO lv_val INDEX lv_even_pos.
        IF sy-subrc = 0.
          APPEND lv_val TO rt_list.
        ENDIF.
        lv_even_pos = lv_even_pos + 1.
      ENDIF.
    ENDDO.
  ENDMETHOD.
ENDCLASS.

CLASS zcl_add_elements IMPLEMENTATION.

  METHOD add_elements.
    FIELD-SYMBOLS: <lt_arr> TYPE ANY TABLE,
                   <lv_val> TYPE any.

    DATA: lv_total TYPE i,
          lv_limit TYPE i,
          lv_idx   TYPE i,
          lv_int   TYPE i,
          lv_abs   TYPE i.

    rv_sum = 0.

    ASSIGN arr TO <lt_arr>.
    IF <lt_arr> IS NOT ASSIGNED.
      RETURN.
    ENDIF.

    lv_total = lines( <lt_arr> ).
    lv_limit = k.
    IF lv_limit > lv_total.
      lv_limit = lv_total.
    ENDIF.
    IF lv_limit <= 0.
      RETURN.
    ENDIF.

    lv_idx = 0.
    LOOP AT <lt_arr> ASSIGNING <lv_val>.
      lv_idx = lv_idx + 1.
      IF lv_idx > lv_limit.
        EXIT.
      ENDIF.

      TRY.
          lv_int = <lv_val>.
        CATCH cx_sy_move_cast_error cx_sy_conversion_no_number cx_sy_conversion_overflow.
          CONTINUE.
      ENDTRY.

      lv_abs = lv_int.
      IF lv_abs < 0.
        lv_abs = 0 - lv_abs.
      ENDIF.

      IF lv_abs < 100.
        rv_sum = rv_sum + lv_int.
      ENDIF.
    ENDLOOP.
  ENDMETHOD.

ENDCLASS.

CLASS zcl_largest_smallest_ints IMPLEMENTATION.

    DATA lv_has_pos TYPE abap_bool VALUE abap_false.
    DATA lv_max_neg TYPE integer.
    DATA lv_min_pos TYPE integer.

    LOOP AT it_list ASSIGNING FIELD-SYMBOL(<n>).
      IF <n> < 0.
        IF lv_has_neg = abap_false OR <n> > lv_max_neg.
          lv_max_neg = <n>.
          lv_has_neg = abap_true.
        ENDIF.
      ELSEIF <n> > 0.
        IF lv_has_pos = abap_false OR <n> < lv_min_pos.
          lv_min_pos = <n>.
          lv_has_pos = abap_true.
        ENDIF.
      ENDIF.
    ENDLOOP.

    IF lv_has_neg = abap_true.
      rs_result = |({ lv_max_neg }, |.
    ELSE.
      rs_result = |(None, |.
    ENDIF.

    IF lv_has_pos = abap_true.
      rs_result = rs_result && |{ lv_min_pos })|.
    ELSE.
      rs_result = rs_result && |None)|.
    ENDIF.
  ENDMETHOD.

CLASS zcl_fizz_buzz DEFINITION

  FINAL
  CREATE PUBLIC.

  PUBLIC SECTION.
    INTERFACES z_humaneval_036.

CLASS zcl_fizz_buzz IMPLEMENTATION.
  METHOD z_humaneval_036~fizz_buzz.
    DATA count TYPE i VALUE 0.
    DATA i TYPE i.
    DATA s TYPE string.
    DATA pos TYPE i.
    DATA len TYPE i.

    IF n <= 0.
      result = 0.
      RETURN.
    ENDIF.

    DO n TIMES.
      i = sy-index - 1.

      IF ( i MOD 11 = 0 ) OR ( i MOD 13 = 0 ).
        s = |{ i }|.
        len = strlen( s ).
        pos = 0.

        WHILE pos < len.
          IF s+pos(1) = '7'.
            count = count + 1.
          ENDIF.
          pos = pos + 1.
        ENDWHILE.
      ENDIF.
    ENDDO.

    result = count.
  ENDMETHOD.
ENDCLASS.

        DO lv_len TIMES.

CLASS zcl_filter_integers IMPLEMENTATION.
  METHOD filter_integers.
    DATA lr_data TYPE REF TO data.
    FIELD-SYMBOLS <lv_any> TYPE any.
    FIELD-SYMBOLS <lv_i>   TYPE i.

    LOOP AT it_values ASSIGNING <lv_any>.
      GET REFERENCE OF <lv_any> INTO lr_data.

      TRY.
          ASSIGN lr_data->* TO <lv_i> CASTING.
          IF sy-subrc = 0.
            APPEND <lv_i> TO rt_integers.
          ENDIF.
        CATCH cx_sy_assign_cast_illegal_cast.
      ENDTRY.
    ENDLOOP.
  ENDMETHOD.
ENDCLASS.

CLASS zcl_filter_integers DEFINITION
  PUBLIC
  FINAL
  CREATE PUBLIC.

  PUBLIC SECTION.
    TYPES ty_integers TYPE STANDARD TABLE OF i WITH EMPTY KEY.

    CLASS-METHODS filter_integers
      IMPORTING
        it_values TYPE ANY TABLE
      RETURNING
        VALUE(rt_integers) TYPE ty_integers.
ENDCLASS.

CLASS zcl_filter_integers IMPLEMENTATION.
  METHOD filter_integers.
    rt_integers = VALUE #( ).

    FIELD-SYMBOLS <lv_any> TYPE any.
    LOOP AT it_values ASSIGNING <lv_any>.
      DATA(lv_kind) = cl_abap_typedescr=>describe_by_data( <lv_any> )->type_kind.

      IF lv_kind <> cl_abap_typedescr=>typekind_int
         AND lv_kind <> cl_abap_typedescr=>typekind_int1
         AND lv_kind <> cl_abap_typedescr=>typekind_int2
         AND lv_kind <> cl_abap_typedescr=>typekind_int8.
        CONTINUE.
      ENDIF.

      TRY.
          APPEND CONV i( <lv_any> ) TO rt_integers.
        CATCH cx_sy_conversion_overflow.
      ENDTRY.
    ENDLOOP.
  ENDMETHOD.
ENDCLASS.

CLASS zcl_filter_integers DEFINITION
  PUBLIC
  FINAL
  CREATE PUBLIC.

  PUBLIC SECTION.
    CLASS-METHODS filter_integers
      IMPORTING
        it_values TYPE STANDARD TABLE OF text255 WITH EMPTY KEY
      RETURNING
        VALUE(rt_result) TYPE STANDARD TABLE OF i WITH EMPTY KEY.
ENDCLASS.

CLASS zcl_filter_integers IMPLEMENTATION.
  METHOD filter_integers.
    rt_result = VALUE #( ).

    LOOP AT it_values INTO DATA(lv_value).
      DATA(lv_trim) = lv_value.
      SHIFT lv_trim LEFT DELETING LEADING space.
      SHIFT lv_trim RIGHT DELETING TRAILING space.

      IF lv_trim IS INITIAL.
        CONTINUE.
      ENDIF.

      IF lv_trim CO `+-0123456789` AND lv_trim CA `0123456789`.
        TRY.
            DATA(lv_i) = CONV i( lv_trim ).
            APPEND lv_i TO rt_result.
          CATCH cx_sy_conversion_no_number
                cx_sy_conversion_overflow.
            CONTINUE.
        ENDTRY.
      ENDIF.
    ENDLOOP.
  ENDMETHOD.
ENDCLASS.

  PUBLIC

  CREATE PUBLIC.

      IMPORTING

      RETURNING
