CLASS zcl_is_sorted DEFINITION
  PUBLIC
  FINAL
  CREATE PUBLIC.

  PUBLIC SECTION.
    CLASS-METHODS is_sorted
      IMPORTING
        it_list        TYPE STANDARD TABLE
      RETURNING
        VALUE(rv_bool) TYPE abap_bool.
ENDCLASS.

CLASS zcl_is_sorted IMPLEMENTATION.
  METHOD is_sorted.
    rv_bool = abap_true.

    DATA lv_prev      TYPE i.
    DATA lv_curr      TYPE i.
    DATA lv_dup_count TYPE i VALUE 1.

    FIELD-SYMBOLS <lv_any> TYPE any.

    IF lines( it_list ) <= 1.
      RETURN.
    ENDIF.

    READ TABLE it_list INDEX 1 ASSIGNING <lv_any>.
    IF sy-subrc <> 0.
      RETURN.
    ENDIF.
    lv_prev = CONV i( <lv_any> ).

    DO lines( it_list ) - 1 TIMES.
      READ TABLE it_list INDEX sy-index + 1 ASSIGNING <lv_any>.
      IF sy-subrc <> 0.
        EXIT.
      ENDIF.
      lv_curr = CONV i( <lv_any> ).

      IF lv_curr < lv_prev.
        rv_bool = abap_false.
        RETURN.
      ENDIF.

      IF lv_curr = lv_prev.
        lv_dup_count = lv_dup_count + 1.
        IF lv_dup_count > 2.
          rv_bool = abap_false.
          RETURN.
        ENDIF.
      ELSE.
        lv_dup_count = 1.
      ENDIF.

      lv_prev = lv_curr.
    ENDDO.
  ENDMETHOD.
ENDCLASS.

CLASS zcl_is_sorted DEFINITION
  PUBLIC
  FINAL
  CREATE PUBLIC.

  PUBLIC SECTION.
    CLASS-METHODS is_sorted
      IMPORTING
        it_list TYPE ANY TABLE
      RETURNING
        VALUE(rv_is_sorted) TYPE abap_bool.
ENDCLASS.

CLASS zcl_is_sorted IMPLEMENTATION.
  METHOD is_sorted.
    rv_is_sorted = abap_true.

    FIELD-SYMBOLS <lv_any> TYPE any.

    DATA lv_prev     TYPE i.
    DATA lv_curr     TYPE i.
    DATA lv_first    TYPE abap_bool VALUE abap_true.
    DATA lv_dup_run  TYPE i VALUE 1.

    LOOP AT it_list ASSIGNING <lv_any>.
      TRY.
          lv_curr = CONV i( <lv_any> ).
        CATCH cx_sy_conversion_no_number cx_sy_move_cast_error.
          rv_is_sorted = abap_false.
          RETURN.
      ENDTRY.

      IF lv_first = abap_true.
        lv_prev  = lv_curr.
        lv_first = abap_false.
        lv_dup_run = 1.
        CONTINUE.
      ENDIF.

      IF lv_curr < lv_prev.
        rv_is_sorted = abap_false.
        RETURN.
      ENDIF.

      IF lv_curr = lv_prev.
        lv_dup_run = lv_dup_run + 1.
        IF lv_dup_run > 2.
          rv_is_sorted = abap_false.
          RETURN.
        ENDIF.
      ELSE.
        lv_dup_run = 1.
      ENDIF.

      lv_prev = lv_curr.
    ENDLOOP.
  ENDMETHOD.
ENDCLASS.

CLASS zcl_is_sorted DEFINITION
  PUBLIC
  FINAL
  CREATE PUBLIC.

  PUBLIC SECTION.
    CLASS-METHODS is_sorted
      IMPORTING
        it_list TYPE ANY TABLE
      RETURNING
        VALUE(rv_is_sorted) TYPE abap_bool.
ENDCLASS.

CLASS zcl_is_sorted IMPLEMENTATION.
  METHOD is_sorted.
    rv_is_sorted = abap_true.

    FIELD-SYMBOLS <n> TYPE any.

    DATA lv_prev      TYPE int8.
    DATA lv_run_value TYPE int8.
    DATA lv_run_len   TYPE int8 VALUE 0.
    DATA lv_first     TYPE abap_bool VALUE abap_true.
    DATA lv_curr      TYPE int8.

    LOOP AT it_list ASSIGNING <n>.
      TRY.
          lv_curr = CONV int8( <n> ).
        CATCH cx_sy_conversion_no_number cx_sy_conversion_overflow.
          rv_is_sorted = abap_false.
          RETURN.
      ENDTRY.

      IF lv_first = abap_true.
        lv_first = abap_false.
        lv_prev = lv_curr.
        lv_run_value = lv_curr.
        lv_run_len = 1.
        CONTINUE.
      ENDIF.

      IF lv_curr < lv_prev.
        rv_is_sorted = abap_false.
        RETURN.
      ENDIF.

      IF lv_curr = lv_run_value.
        lv_run_len = lv_run_len + 1.
        IF lv_run_len > 2.
          rv_is_sorted = abap_false.
          RETURN.
        ENDIF.
      ELSE.
        lv_run_value = lv_curr.
        lv_run_len = 1.
      ENDIF.

      lv_prev = lv_curr.
    ENDLOOP.
  ENDMETHOD.
ENDCLASS.

CLASS zcl_sort_third DEFINITION
  PUBLIC
  FINAL
  CREATE PUBLIC.

  PUBLIC SECTION.
    TYPES: BEGIN OF ty_line,
             value TYPE p LENGTH 16 DECIMALS 0,
           END OF ty_line.
    TYPES ty_list TYPE STANDARD TABLE OF ty_line WITH DEFAULT KEY.

    CLASS-METHODS sort_third
      IMPORTING
        it_list TYPE ty_list
      RETURNING
        VALUE(rt_list) TYPE ty_list.
ENDCLASS.

CLASS zcl_sort_third IMPLEMENTATION.
  METHOD sort_third.
    rt_list = it_list.

    DATA lt_third TYPE STANDARD TABLE OF ty_line WITH EMPTY KEY.
    DATA ls_line  TYPE ty_line.
    DATA lv_idx   TYPE i.

    LOOP AT rt_list INTO ls_line.
      lv_idx = sy-tabix.
      IF ( lv_idx - 1 ) MOD 3 = 0.
        APPEND ls_line TO lt_third.
      ENDIF.
    ENDLOOP.

    SORT lt_third BY value ASCENDING.

    DATA lv_pos TYPE i VALUE 0.
    LOOP AT rt_list INTO ls_line.
      lv_idx = sy-tabix.
      IF ( lv_idx - 1 ) MOD 3 = 0.
        lv_pos = lv_pos + 1.
        READ TABLE lt_third INDEX lv_pos INTO ls_line.
        MODIFY rt_list FROM ls_line INDEX lv_idx.
      ENDIF.
    ENDLOOP.
  ENDMETHOD.
ENDCLASS.

CLASS zcl_sort_third DEFINITION
  PUBLIC
  FINAL
  CREATE PUBLIC.

  PUBLIC SECTION.
    TYPES tt_int TYPE STANDARD TABLE OF syindex WITH NON-UNIQUE DEFAULT KEY.

    CLASS-METHODS sort_third
      IMPORTING
        it_list        TYPE tt_int
      RETURNING
        VALUE(rt_list) TYPE tt_int.
ENDCLASS.

CLASS zcl_sort_third IMPLEMENTATION.
  METHOD sort_third.
    rt_list = it_list.

    DATA lt_third_vals TYPE tt_int.
    DATA lv_idx        TYPE sy-tabix.

    LOOP AT rt_list ASSIGNING FIELD-SYMBOL(<v>).
      lv_idx = sy-tabix.
      IF ( lv_idx - 1 ) MOD 3 = 0.
        APPEND <v> TO lt_third_vals.
      ENDIF.
    ENDLOOP.

    SORT lt_third_vals.

    DATA lv_pos TYPE syindex VALUE 0.
    LOOP AT rt_list ASSIGNING <v>.
      lv_idx = sy-tabix.
      IF ( lv_idx - 1 ) MOD 3 = 0.
        lv_pos = lv_pos + 1.
        READ TABLE lt_third_vals INDEX lv_pos INTO DATA(lv_new).
        IF sy-subrc = 0.
          <v> = lv_new.
        ENDIF.
      ENDIF.
    ENDLOOP.
  ENDMETHOD.
ENDCLASS.

CLASS zcl_sort_third DEFINITION
  PUBLIC
  FINAL
  CREATE PUBLIC.

  PUBLIC SECTION.
    TYPES ty_int TYPE int1.
    TYPES ty_int_tab TYPE STANDARD TABLE OF ty_int WITH EMPTY KEY.

    CLASS-METHODS sort_third
      IMPORTING
        it_list TYPE ty_int_tab
      RETURNING
        VALUE(rt_list) TYPE ty_int_tab.
ENDCLASS.

CLASS zcl_sort_third IMPLEMENTATION.
  METHOD sort_third.
    rt_list = it_list.

    DATA lt_third TYPE SORTED TABLE OF ty_int WITH UNIQUE KEY table_line.
    DATA lv_idx TYPE i VALUE 0.

    LOOP AT rt_list ASSIGNING FIELD-SYMBOL(<v>).
      IF lv_idx MOD 3 = 0.
        INSERT <v> INTO TABLE lt_third.
      ENDIF.
      lv_idx = lv_idx + 1.
    ENDLOOP.

    DATA lv_third_pos TYPE i VALUE 1.
    lv_idx = 0.

    LOOP AT rt_list ASSIGNING <v>.
      IF lv_idx MOD 3 = 0.
        READ TABLE lt_third INDEX lv_third_pos ASSIGNING FIELD-SYMBOL(<t>).
        IF sy-subrc = 0.
          <v> = <t>.
        ENDIF.
        lv_third_pos = lv_third_pos + 1.
      ENDIF.
      lv_idx = lv_idx + 1.
    ENDLOOP.
  ENDMETHOD.
ENDCLASS.

CLASS zcl_flip_case DEFINITION
  PUBLIC
  FINAL
  CREATE PUBLIC.

  PUBLIC SECTION.
    CLASS-METHODS flip_case
      IMPORTING
        i_string TYPE string
      RETURNING
        VALUE(r_result) TYPE string.
ENDCLASS.

CLASS zcl_flip_case IMPLEMENTATION.
  METHOD flip_case.
    DATA: lv_len  TYPE i,
          lv_idx  TYPE i,
          lv_char TYPE c LENGTH 1,
          lv_out  TYPE c LENGTH 1.

    lv_len = strlen( i_string ).
    r_result = ``.

    lv_idx = 0.
    WHILE lv_idx < lv_len.
      lv_char = i_string+lv_idx(1).
      lv_out  = lv_char.

      IF lv_char CO 'abcdefghijklmnopqrstuvwxyz'.
        TRANSLATE lv_out TO UPPER CASE.
      ELSEIF lv_char CO 'ABCDEFGHIJKLMNOPQRSTUVWXYZ'.
        TRANSLATE lv_out TO LOWER CASE.
      ENDIF.

      r_result = r_result && lv_out.
      lv_idx = lv_idx + 1.
    ENDWHILE.
  ENDMETHOD.
ENDCLASS.

CLASS zcl_flip_case DEFINITION
  PUBLIC
  FINAL
  CREATE PUBLIC.

  PUBLIC SECTION.
    CLASS-METHODS flip_case
      IMPORTING
        i_string TYPE string
      RETURNING
        VALUE(r_string) TYPE string.
ENDCLASS.

CLASS zcl_flip_case IMPLEMENTATION.
  METHOD flip_case.
    DATA lv_len       TYPE i.
    DATA lv_idx       TYPE i.
    DATA lv_in_char   TYPE c LENGTH 1.
    DATA lv_out_char  TYPE c LENGTH 1.

    lv_len = strlen( i_string ).
    r_string = ``.

    DO lv_len TIMES.
      lv_idx = sy-index - 1.
      lv_in_char = i_string+lv_idx(1).
      lv_out_char = lv_in_char.

      IF lv_in_char BETWEEN 'A' AND 'Z'.
        TRANSLATE lv_out_char TO LOWER CASE.
      ELSEIF lv_in_char BETWEEN 'a' AND 'z'.
        TRANSLATE lv_out_char TO UPPER CASE.
      ENDIF.

      r_string = r_string && lv_out_char.
    ENDDO.
  ENDMETHOD.
ENDCLASS.

CLASS zcl_flip_case DEFINITION
  PUBLIC
  FINAL
  CREATE PUBLIC.

  PUBLIC SECTION.
    CLASS-METHODS flip_case
      IMPORTING
        iv_string TYPE string
      RETURNING
        VALUE(rv_string) TYPE string.
ENDCLASS.

CLASS zcl_flip_case IMPLEMENTATION.
  METHOD flip_case.
    DATA lv_len  TYPE i.
    DATA lv_char TYPE c LENGTH 1.
    DATA lv_idx  TYPE i.

    lv_len = strlen( iv_string ).
    rv_string = ``.

    lv_idx = 0.
    WHILE lv_idx < lv_len.
      lv_char = iv_string+lv_idx(1).

      IF lv_char = ` `.
        rv_string = rv_string && ` `.
      ELSEIF lv_char CA `ABCDEFGHIJKLMNOPQRSTUVWXYZ`.
        TRANSLATE lv_char TO LOWER CASE.
        rv_string = rv_string && lv_char.
      ELSEIF lv_char CA `abcdefghijklmnopqrstuvwxyz`.
        TRANSLATE lv_char TO UPPER CASE.
        rv_string = rv_string && lv_char.
      ELSE.
        rv_string = rv_string && lv_char.
      ENDIF.

      lv_idx = lv_idx + 1.
    ENDWHILE.
  ENDMETHOD.

CLASS zcl_flip_case DEFINITION
  PUBLIC
  FINAL
  CREATE PUBLIC.

  PUBLIC SECTION.
    CLASS-METHODS flip_case
      IMPORTING
        i_string TYPE string
      RETURNING
        VALUE(r_string) TYPE string.
ENDCLASS.

CLASS zcl_flip_case IMPLEMENTATION.
  METHOD flip_case.
    DATA lv_len     TYPE i.
    DATA lv_idx     TYPE i.
    DATA lv_char    TYPE c LENGTH 1.
    DATA lv_cp      TYPE i.
    DATA lv_unicode TYPE c LENGTH 4.

    lv_len = strlen( i_string ).
    CLEAR r_string.

    lv_idx = 0.
    WHILE lv_idx < lv_len.
      lv_char = i_string+lv_idx(1).

      IF lv_char = space.
        r_string = r_string && space.
        lv_idx = lv_idx + 1.
        CONTINUE.
      ENDIF.

      lv_cp = cl_abap_conv_in_ce=>uccp( lv_char ).

      IF lv_cp BETWEEN 97 AND 122.
        lv_cp = lv_cp - 32.
      ELSEIF lv_cp BETWEEN 65 AND 90.
        lv_cp = lv_cp + 32.
      ENDIF.

      lv_unicode = lv_cp.
      r_string = r_string && cl_abap_conv_out_ce=>uccp( lv_unicode ).

      lv_idx = lv_idx + 1.
    ENDWHILE.
  ENDMETHOD.
ENDCLASS.

    DO lv_len TIMES.

      ELSEIF lv_char CO 'ABCDEFGHIJKLMNOPQRSTUVWXYZ'.
        TRANSLATE lv_char TO LOWER CASE.

CLASS zcl_flip_case DEFINITION
  PUBLIC
  FINAL
  CREATE PUBLIC.

  PUBLIC SECTION.
    CLASS-METHODS flip_case
      IMPORTING
        iv_string TYPE string
      RETURNING
        VALUE(rv_string) TYPE string.
ENDCLASS.

CLASS zcl_flip_case IMPLEMENTATION.
  METHOD flip_case.
    DATA: lv_len      TYPE i,
          lv_idx      TYPE i,
          lv_char     TYPE c LENGTH 1,
          lv_cp       TYPE i,
          lv_new_cp   TYPE i,
          lv_new_char TYPE c LENGTH 1.

    lv_len = strlen( iv_string ).
    rv_string = ``.

    DO lv_len TIMES.
      lv_idx = sy-index - 1.
      lv_char = iv_string+lv_idx(1).

        lv_new_cp = lv_cp + 32.
        lv_new_char = cl_abap_conv_out_ce=>uccp( lv_new_cp ).
        rv_string = rv_string && lv_new_char.
      ELSEIF lv_cp BETWEEN 97 AND 122.
        lv_new_cp = lv_cp - 32.
        lv_new_char = cl_abap_conv_out_ce=>uccp( lv_new_cp ).
        rv_string = rv_string && lv_new_char.
      ELSE.
        rv_string = rv_string && lv_char.
      ENDIF.

  ENDMETHOD.

CLASS zcl_get_closest_vowel DEFINITION
  PUBLIC
  FINAL
  CREATE PUBLIC.

  PUBLIC SECTION.
    CLASS-METHODS get_closest_vowel
      IMPORTING
        iv_word TYPE string
      RETURNING
        VALUE(rv_vowel) TYPE string.
ENDCLASS.

CLASS zcl_get_closest_vowel IMPLEMENTATION.
  METHOD get_closest_vowel.
    DATA: lv_len TYPE i,
          lv_pos TYPE i,
          lv_left  TYPE c LENGTH 1,
          lv_mid   TYPE c LENGTH 1,
          lv_right TYPE c LENGTH 1,
          lv_left_u  TYPE c LENGTH 1,
          lv_mid_u   TYPE c LENGTH 1,
          lv_right_u TYPE c LENGTH 1.

    rv_vowel = ''.
    lv_len = strlen( iv_word ).

    IF lv_len < 3.
      RETURN.
    ENDIF.

    lv_pos = lv_len - 2.

    WHILE lv_pos >= 2.
      lv_left  = iv_word+lv_pos-1(1).
      lv_mid   = iv_word+lv_pos(1).
      lv_right = iv_word+lv_pos+1(1).

      lv_left_u = lv_left.
      lv_mid_u = lv_mid.
      lv_right_u = lv_right.

      TRANSLATE lv_left_u TO UPPER CASE.
      TRANSLATE lv_mid_u TO UPPER CASE.
      TRANSLATE lv_right_u TO UPPER CASE.

      IF lv_mid_u CA 'AEIOU' AND NOT ( lv_left_u CA 'AEIOU' ) AND NOT ( lv_right_u CA 'AEIOU' ).
        rv_vowel = lv_mid.
        RETURN.
      ENDIF.

      lv_pos = lv_pos - 1.
    ENDWHILE.
  ENDMETHOD.
ENDCLASS.

CLASS zcl_tribonacci DEFINITION
  PUBLIC
  FINAL
  CREATE PUBLIC.

  PUBLIC SECTION.
    TYPES ty_t_int8 TYPE STANDARD TABLE OF int8 WITH EMPTY KEY.

    CLASS-METHODS tri
      IMPORTING
        n TYPE i
      RETURNING
        VALUE(rt_values) TYPE ty_t_int8.
ENDCLASS.

CLASS zcl_tribonacci IMPLEMENTATION.
  METHOD tri.
    DATA lt_values TYPE ty_t_int8.
    DATA lv_n TYPE i.
    DATA lv_k TYPE i.
    DATA lv_val TYPE int8.

    lv_n = n.

    IF lv_n < 0.
      RETURN.
    ENDIF.

    DO lv_n + 3 TIMES.
      APPEND 0 TO lt_values.
    ENDDO.

    lt_values[ 1 ] = 1.
    lt_values[ 2 ] = 3.

    DO lv_n + 1 TIMES.
      lv_k = sy-index + 1.
      IF lv_k MOD 2 = 0.
        lv_val = 1 + lv_k / 2.
        lt_values[ lv_k + 1 ] = lv_val.
      ENDIF.
    ENDDO.

    DO lv_n + 1 TIMES.
      lv_k = sy-index + 2.
      IF lv_k MOD 2 = 1 AND lv_k <= lv_n.
        lv_val = lt_values[ lv_k ] + lt_values[ lv_k - 1 ] + lt_values[ lv_k + 2 ].
        lt_values[ lv_k + 1 ] = lv_val.
      ENDIF.
    ENDDO.

    rt_values = VALUE ty_t_int8(
      FOR lv_i = 0 THEN lv_i + 1 UNTIL lv_i > lv_n
      ( lt_values[ lv_i + 1 ] )
    ).
  ENDMETHOD.
ENDCLASS.

CLASS zcl_tribonacci DEFINITION
  PUBLIC
  FINAL
  CREATE PUBLIC.

  PUBLIC SECTION.
    TYPES ty_values TYPE STANDARD TABLE OF int8 WITH EMPTY KEY.

    CLASS-METHODS tri
      IMPORTING
        n TYPE i
      RETURNING
        VALUE(rt_values) TYPE ty_values.
ENDCLASS.

CLASS zcl_tribonacci IMPLEMENTATION.
  METHOD tri.
    DATA lv_max_even TYPE i.
    DATA lv_even_n   TYPE i.
    DATA lv_odd_n    TYPE i.

    rt_values = VALUE ty_values( ).

    IF n < 0.
      RETURN.
    ENDIF.

    rt_values = VALUE ty_values(
      FOR i = 0 THEN i + 1 WHILE i <= n
      ( CONV int8( 0 ) )
    ).

    rt_values[ 1 ] = CONV int8( 1 ).
    IF n >= 1.
      rt_values[ 2 ] = CONV int8( 3 ).
    ENDIF.

    lv_max_even = n.
    IF lv_max_even MOD 2 = 1.
      lv_max_even = lv_max_even - 1.
    ENDIF.

    IF lv_max_even >= 2.
      DO lv_max_even DIV 2 TIMES.
        lv_even_n = sy-index * 2.
        rt_values[ lv_even_n + 1 ] = CONV int8( 1 + lv_even_n DIV 2 ).
      ENDDO.
    ENDIF.

    lv_odd_n = 3.
    WHILE lv_odd_n <= n.
      rt_values[ lv_odd_n + 1 ] =
        rt_values[ lv_odd_n ] +
        rt_values[ lv_odd_n - 1 ] +
        rt_values[ lv_odd_n + 2 ].
      lv_odd_n = lv_odd_n + 2.
    ENDWHILE.
  ENDMETHOD.
ENDCLASS.

CLASS zcl_tribonacci DEFINITION
  PUBLIC
  FINAL
  CREATE PUBLIC.

  PUBLIC SECTION.
    TYPES ty_seq TYPE STANDARD TABLE OF i WITH EMPTY KEY.

    CLASS-METHODS get_sequence
      IMPORTING
        iv_n TYPE i
      RETURNING
        VALUE(rt_seq) TYPE ty_seq.
ENDCLASS.

CLASS zcl_tribonacci IMPLEMENTATION.
  METHOD get_sequence.
    rt_seq = VALUE #( ).

    IF iv_n < 0.
      RETURN.
    ENDIF.

    DATA lv_i   TYPE i.
    DATA lv_val TYPE i.

    DO iv_n + 1 TIMES.
      lv_i = sy-index - 1.

      IF lv_i = 0.
        lv_val = 1.
      ELSEIF lv_i = 1.
        lv_val = 3.
      ELSEIF lv_i MOD 2 = 0.
        lv_val = 1 + lv_i / 2.
      ELSE.
        lv_val = ( lv_i + 1 ) * ( lv_i + 1 ) - 1.
      ENDIF.

      APPEND lv_val TO rt_seq.
    ENDDO.
  ENDMETHOD.
ENDCLASS.

CLASS zcl_tribonacci DEFINITION
  PUBLIC
  FINAL
  CREATE PUBLIC.

  PUBLIC SECTION.
    TYPES ty_int_tab TYPE STANDARD TABLE OF i WITH EMPTY KEY.

    CLASS-METHODS tri
      IMPORTING
        n TYPE i
      RETURNING
        VALUE(rt_values) TYPE ty_int_tab.
ENDCLASS.

CLASS zcl_tribonacci IMPLEMENTATION.
  METHOD tri.
    rt_values = VALUE #( ).

    IF n < 0.
      RETURN.
    ENDIF.

    DATA lt_vals TYPE ty_int_tab.
    DATA: lv_i     TYPE i,
          lv_max_n TYPE i.

    lv_max_n = n + 2.

    DO lv_max_n + 1 TIMES.
      APPEND 0 TO lt_vals.
    ENDDO.

    lt_vals[ 1 ] = 1.
    lt_vals[ 2 ] = 3.

    DO lv_max_n TIMES.
      lv_i = sy-index.
      IF lv_i >= 2 AND ( lv_i MOD 2 ) = 0.
        lt_vals[ lv_i + 1 ] = 1 + ( lv_i / 2 ).
      ENDIF.
    ENDDO.

    DO lv_max_n TIMES.
      lv_i = sy-index.
      IF lv_i >= 3 AND ( lv_i MOD 2 ) = 1.
        IF lv_i + 2 <= lines( lt_vals ).
          lt_vals[ lv_i + 1 ] = lt_vals[ lv_i ] + lt_vals[ lv_i - 1 ] + lt_vals[ lv_i + 2 ].
        ENDIF.
      ENDIF.
    ENDDO.

    rt_values = VALUE #( FOR idx = 0 THEN idx + 1 UNTIL idx > n ( lt_vals[ idx + 1 ] ) ).
  ENDMETHOD.
ENDCLASS.

CLASS zcl_split_words DEFINITION
  PUBLIC
  FINAL
  CREATE PUBLIC.

  PUBLIC SECTION.
    CLASS-METHODS split_words
      IMPORTING
        txt TYPE string
      RETURNING
        VALUE(rt_words) TYPE string_table.
ENDCLASS.

CLASS zcl_split_words IMPLEMENTATION.
  METHOD split_words.
    DATA lt_words TYPE string_table.
    DATA lv_has_space TYPE abap_bool VALUE abap_false.
    DATA lv_has_comma TYPE abap_bool VALUE abap_false.

    IF txt CS ` `
       OR txt CS cl_abap_char_utilities=>horizontal_tab
       OR txt CS cl_abap_char_utilities=>newline
       OR txt CS cl_abap_char_utilities=>cr_lf.
      lv_has_space = abap_true.
    ENDIF.

    IF txt CS `,`.
      lv_has_comma = abap_true.
    ENDIF.

    IF lv_has_space = abap_true.
      SPLIT txt AT space INTO TABLE lt_words.
      DELETE lt_words WHERE table_line IS INITIAL.
      rt_words = lt_words.
      RETURN.
    ENDIF.

    IF lv_has_comma = abap_true.
      SPLIT txt AT `,` INTO TABLE lt_words.
      rt_words = lt_words.
      RETURN.
    ENDIF.

    DATA lv_count TYPE i VALUE 0.
    DATA lv_len   TYPE i.
    DATA lv_off   TYPE i.
    DATA lv_c     TYPE c LENGTH 1.
    DATA lv_ord   TYPE i.

    lv_len = strlen( txt ).

    DO lv_len TIMES.
      lv_off = sy-index - 1.
      lv_c = txt+lv_off(1).
      IF lv_c CO `abcdefghijklmnopqrstuvwxyz`.
        lv_ord = find( val = `abcdefghijklmnopqrstuvwxyz` sub = lv_c ).
        IF lv_ord >= 0 AND ( lv_ord MOD 2 ) = 1.
          lv_count = lv_count + 1.
        ENDIF.
      ENDIF.
    ENDDO.

    APPEND |{ lv_count }| TO rt_words.
  ENDMETHOD.
ENDCLASS.

CLASS zcl_split_words DEFINITION
  PUBLIC
  FINAL
  CREATE PUBLIC.

  PUBLIC SECTION.
    CLASS-METHODS split_words
      IMPORTING
        txt TYPE string
      RETURNING
        VALUE(rt_words) TYPE string_table.
ENDCLASS.

CLASS zcl_split_words IMPLEMENTATION.
  METHOD split_words.
    rt_words = VALUE string_table( ).

    IF txt IS INITIAL.
      RETURN.
    ENDIF.

    IF txt CS space.
      SPLIT txt AT space INTO TABLE rt_words.
      DELETE rt_words WHERE table_line IS INITIAL.
      RETURN.
    ENDIF.

    IF txt CS `,`.
      SPLIT txt AT `,` INTO TABLE rt_words.
      DELETE rt_words WHERE table_line IS INITIAL.
      RETURN.
    ENDIF.

    DATA(lv_count) = 0.
    DATA(lv_len) = strlen( txt ).

    DO lv_len TIMES.
      DATA(lv_off) = sy-index - 1.
      DATA(lv_char) = txt+lv_off(1).
      TRANSLATE lv_char TO LOWER CASE.

      IF lv_char CO `abcdefghijklmnopqrstuvwxyz`.
        DATA(lv_code) = ( cl_abap_conv_out_ce=>uccpi( lv_char ) - cl_abap_conv_out_ce=>uccpi( `a` ) ).
        IF ( lv_code MOD 2 ) = 0.
          lv_count = lv_count + 1.
        ENDIF.
      ENDIF.
    ENDDO.

    rt_words = VALUE string_table( ( |{ lv_count }| ) ).
  ENDMETHOD.
ENDCLASS.

CLASS zcl_split_words DEFINITION
  PUBLIC
  FINAL
  CREATE PUBLIC.

  PUBLIC SECTION.
    CLASS-METHODS split_words
      IMPORTING
        !iv_txt TYPE string
      RETURNING
        VALUE(rt_words) TYPE string_table.
ENDCLASS.

CLASS zcl_split_words IMPLEMENTATION.
  METHOD split_words.
    DATA lt_words TYPE string_table.
    DATA lv_txt   TYPE string.

    IF iv_txt IS INITIAL.
      CLEAR rt_words.
      RETURN.
    ENDIF.

    lv_txt = iv_txt.

    FIND FIRST OCCURRENCE OF REGEX '\s' IN lv_txt.
    IF sy-subrc = 0.
      SPLIT lv_txt AT REGEX '\s+' INTO TABLE lt_words.
      DELETE lt_words WHERE table_line IS INITIAL.
      rt_words = lt_words.
      RETURN.
    ENDIF.

    IF lv_txt CS ','.
      SPLIT lv_txt AT ',' INTO TABLE lt_words.
      DELETE lt_words WHERE table_line IS INITIAL.
      rt_words = lt_words.
      RETURN.
    ENDIF.

    DATA lv_count TYPE i VALUE 0.
    DATA lv_i     TYPE i VALUE 0.
    DATA lv_len   TYPE i.
    DATA lv_c     TYPE c LENGTH 1.
    DATA lv_code  TYPE i.

    TRANSLATE lv_txt TO LOWER CASE.
    lv_len = strlen( lv_txt ).

    WHILE lv_i < lv_len.
      lv_c = lv_txt+lv_i(1).

      IF lv_c CO 'abcdefghijklmnopqrstuvwxyz'.
        lv_code = sy-abcde+lv_code(1).
      ENDIF.

      lv_i = lv_i + 1.
    ENDWHILE.

    lv_count = 0.
    lv_i = 0.

    WHILE lv_i < lv_len.
      lv_c = lv_txt+lv_i(1).
      IF lv_c CO 'abcdefghijklmnopqrstuvwxyz'.
        lv_code = ( cl_abap_conv_out_ce=>uccpi( lv_c ) - cl_abap_conv_out_ce=>uccpi( 'a' ) ) + 1.
        IF lv_code MOD 2 = 0.
          lv_count = lv_count + 1.
        ENDIF.
      ENDIF.
      lv_i = lv_i + 1.
    ENDWHILE.

    rt_words = VALUE string_table( ( |{ lv_count }| ) ).
  ENDMETHOD.
ENDCLASS.

CLASS zcl_split_words DEFINITION
  PUBLIC
  FINAL
  CREATE PUBLIC.

  PUBLIC SECTION.
    CLASS-METHODS split_words
      IMPORTING
        txt TYPE string
      RETURNING
        VALUE(rt_words) TYPE string_table.
ENDCLASS.

CLASS zcl_split_words IMPLEMENTATION.
  METHOD split_words.
    DATA lv_has_space TYPE abap_bool.
    DATA lv_has_comma TYPE abap_bool.
    DATA lv_count     TYPE i.
    DATA lv_pos       TYPE i.
    DATA lv_c         TYPE c LENGTH 1.
    DATA lv_code      TYPE i.

    IF txt IS INITIAL.
      RETURN.
    ENDIF.

    lv_has_space = xsdbool(
         txt CS ` `
      OR txt CA cl_abap_char_utilities=>horizontal_tab
      OR txt CA cl_abap_char_utilities=>cr_lf
      OR txt CA cl_abap_char_utilities=>newline ).

    lv_has_comma = xsdbool( txt CS `,` ).

    IF lv_has_space = abap_true.
      SPLIT txt AT space INTO TABLE rt_words.
      DELETE rt_words WHERE table_line IS INITIAL.
      RETURN.
    ENDIF.

    IF lv_has_comma = abap_true.
      SPLIT txt AT `,` INTO TABLE rt_words.
      DELETE rt_words WHERE table_line IS INITIAL.
      RETURN.
    ENDIF.

    lv_count = 0.
    DO strlen( txt ) TIMES.
      lv_pos = sy-index - 1.
      lv_c = txt+lv_pos(1).
      TRANSLATE lv_c TO LOWER CASE.
      IF lv_c CA `abcdefghijklmnopqrstuvwxyz`.
        lv_code = cl_abap_conv_in_ce=>uccp( lv_c ) - cl_abap_conv_in_ce=>uccp( `a` ).
        IF lv_code MOD 2 = 1.
          lv_count = lv_count + 1.
        ENDIF.
      ENDIF.
    ENDDO.

    APPEND |{ lv_count }| TO rt_words.
  ENDMETHOD.
ENDCLASS.

CLASS zcl_match_parens DEFINITION
  PUBLIC
  FINAL
  CREATE PUBLIC.

  PUBLIC SECTION.
    TYPES ty_str TYPE c LENGTH 10000.
    TYPES ty_str_tab TYPE STANDARD TABLE OF ty_str WITH EMPTY KEY.

    CLASS-METHODS match_parens
      IMPORTING
        it_lst TYPE ty_str_tab
      RETURNING
        VALUE(rv_result) TYPE char3.
ENDCLASS.

CLASS zcl_match_parens IMPLEMENTATION.
  METHOD match_parens.
    DATA lv_s1 TYPE ty_str.
    DATA lv_s2 TYPE ty_str.
    DATA lt_candidates TYPE STANDARD TABLE OF ty_str WITH EMPTY KEY.
    DATA lv_s TYPE ty_str.
    DATA lv_bal TYPE i.
    DATA lv_ok TYPE abap_bool.
    DATA lv_c TYPE c LENGTH 1.

    rv_result = 'No'.

    IF lines( it_lst ) <> 2.
      RETURN.
    ENDIF.

    READ TABLE it_lst INDEX 1 INTO lv_s1.
    READ TABLE it_lst INDEX 2 INTO lv_s2.

    APPEND |{ lv_s1 }{ lv_s2 }| TO lt_candidates.
    APPEND |{ lv_s2 }{ lv_s1 }| TO lt_candidates.

    LOOP AT lt_candidates INTO lv_s.
      lv_bal = 0.
      lv_ok = abap_true.

      DO strlen( lv_s ) TIMES.
        lv_c = lv_s+sy-index(1).

        IF lv_c = '('.
          lv_bal = lv_bal + 1.
        ELSEIF lv_c = ')'.
          lv_bal = lv_bal - 1.
          IF lv_bal < 0.
            lv_ok = abap_false.
            EXIT.
          ENDIF.
        ELSE.
          lv_ok = abap_false.
          EXIT.
        ENDIF.
      ENDDO.

      IF lv_ok = abap_true AND lv_bal = 0.
        rv_result = 'Yes'.
        RETURN.
      ENDIF.
    ENDLOOP.
  ENDMETHOD.
ENDCLASS.

CLASS zcl_match_parens DEFINITION
  PUBLIC
  FINAL
  CREATE PUBLIC.

  PUBLIC SECTION.
    TYPES ty_paren_str TYPE c LENGTH 1000.
    TYPES ty_list TYPE STANDARD TABLE OF ty_paren_str WITH EMPTY KEY.

    CLASS-METHODS match_parens
      IMPORTING
        it_list TYPE ty_list
      RETURNING
        VALUE(rv_result) TYPE c LENGTH 3.
ENDCLASS.

CLASS zcl_match_parens IMPLEMENTATION.
  METHOD match_parens.
    DATA lv_s1 TYPE ty_paren_str.
    DATA lv_s2 TYPE ty_paren_str.

    READ TABLE it_list INDEX 1 INTO lv_s1.
    READ TABLE it_list INDEX 2 INTO lv_s2.

    DATA lv_a TYPE ty_paren_str.
    DATA lv_b TYPE ty_paren_str.

    CONCATENATE lv_s1 lv_s2 INTO lv_a.
    CONCATENATE lv_s2 lv_s1 INTO lv_b.

    DATA lv_good_a TYPE abap_bool VALUE abap_true.
    DATA lv_good_b TYPE abap_bool VALUE abap_true.

    DATA lv_bal TYPE i.

    lv_bal = 0.
    DO strlen( lv_a ) TIMES.
      DATA lv_c TYPE c LENGTH 1.
      lv_c = lv_a+sy-index-1(1).
      IF lv_c = '('.
        lv_bal = lv_bal + 1.
      ELSE.
        lv_bal = lv_bal - 1.
      ENDIF.
      IF lv_bal < 0.
        lv_good_a = abap_false.
        EXIT.
      ENDIF.
    ENDDO.
    IF lv_good_a = abap_true AND lv_bal <> 0.
      lv_good_a = abap_false.
    ENDIF.

    lv_bal = 0.
    DO strlen( lv_b ) TIMES.
      DATA lv_c2 TYPE c LENGTH 1.
      lv_c2 = lv_b+sy-index-1(1).
      IF lv_c2 = '('.
        lv_bal = lv_bal + 1.
      ELSE.
        lv_bal = lv_bal - 1.
      ENDIF.
      IF lv_bal < 0.
        lv_good_b = abap_false.
        EXIT.
      ENDIF.
    ENDDO.
    IF lv_good_b = abap_true AND lv_bal <> 0.
      lv_good_b = abap_false.
    ENDIF.

    IF lv_good_a = abap_true OR lv_good_b = abap_true.
      rv_result = 'Yes'.
    ELSE.
      rv_result = 'No'.
    ENDIF.
  ENDMETHOD.
ENDCLASS.

CLASS zcl_how_many_times DEFINITION
  PUBLIC
  FINAL
  CREATE PUBLIC.

  PUBLIC SECTION.
    CLASS-METHODS how_many_times
      IMPORTING
        VALUE(string)    TYPE string
        VALUE(substring) TYPE string
      RETURNING
        VALUE(rv_count)  TYPE i.
ENDCLASS.

CLASS zcl_how_many_times IMPLEMENTATION.
  METHOD how_many_times.
    DATA: lv_off    TYPE i,
          lv_found  TYPE i,
          lv_len_s  TYPE i,
          lv_len_ss TYPE i.

    rv_count = 0.

    lv_len_s  = strlen( string ).
    lv_len_ss = strlen( substring ).

    IF lv_len_ss = 0 OR lv_len_s = 0 OR lv_len_ss > lv_len_s.
      RETURN.
    ENDIF.

    DO lv_len_s TIMES.
      lv_off = sy-index - 1.
      IF lv_off + lv_len_ss > lv_len_s.
        EXIT.
      ENDIF.

      FIND FIRST OCCURRENCE OF substring IN SECTION OFFSET lv_off LENGTH lv_len_ss OF string
        IN CHARACTER MODE
        MATCH OFFSET lv_found.

      IF sy-subrc = 0 AND lv_found = 0.
        rv_count = rv_count + 1.
      ENDIF.
    ENDDO.
  ENDMETHOD.
ENDCLASS.

CLASS zcl_get_positive IMPLEMENTATION.
